hadiths[173]{hadithnumber,text}:
3776,maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha batlaaiye ( Ansar ( apna naam aap logon ne khud rakh liya tha ya aap logon ka ye naam Allah Taala ne rakha ? unhon-ne kaha nahi balke hamara ye naam Allah Taala ne rakha hai. Ghelaan ki riwayat hai ke ham Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey to aap ham se Ansar ki fazeelatein aur ghazawaat mein unke mujaahidaana waaqiaat bayan kya kartey phir meri taraf ya qabila Azd ke aik shakhs ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar kehtey : tumhari qaum ( Ansar ( ne falan din falan din falan-falan kaam anjam diye.
3777,"Buaas ki jang ko (jo Islam se pahley Aus aur khazraj mein hui thi) Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mafaad mein pahley hi muqaddam kar rakha tha chunanche jab aap Madina mein tashrif laey to ye qabaayel aapas ki phoot ka shikar they aur unke sardaar kuchh qatl kiye ja chukey they, kuchh zakhmi they, to Allah Taala ne us jang ko aap se pahley isliye muqaddam kya tha taake wo aap ke tashrif latey hi musalman ho jaaein."
3778,"fateh Makka ke din jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish ko) jange-Hunain ki) ghaneemat ka Sara maal de diya to kuchh naujawaan ansaariyoon ne kaha (Allah ki qasam!) ye to ajeeb baat hai abhi hamari talwaaron se Quraish ka khoon tapak raha hai aur hamara hasil kya hua maale-ghanimat sirf unhein diya ja raha hai, iski khabar jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mili to aap ne Ansar ko bulaya. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo khabar mujhey mili hai kya wo sahi hai? Ansar log jhoot nahi boltey they unhon-ne arz kar diya ke aapko sahi itlaa mili hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum us se khush aur razi nahi ho ke jab sab log ghaneemat ka maal lekar apne gharon ko wapas hon aur tum log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sath liye apne gharon ko jao gey? Ansar jis naley ya ghaati mein chalengey to main bhi usi naley ya ghaati mein chalun ga."
3779,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ya (yoon bayan kya ke) abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ansar jis wadi ya ghaati mein jayen to main bhi unhiin ki wadi mein jaaunga aur agar main hijrat na karta to main Ansar ka aik fard hona pasand karta. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aap par mere maan-baap qurbaan hon aap ne ye koi zulm wali baat nahi farmai aapko Ansar ne apne yahan thehraya aur aap ki madad ki thi ya Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne (iske hi jaisa) aur koi doosra kalima kahaa.
3780,"jab muhajir log Madina mein aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf aur Sad-bin-Rabee ke darmyan bhai-chara kara diya. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke main Ansar mein sabse zyada daulat mand hun isliye aap mera aadha maal ley lein aur meri 2 beeviyan hain aap unhein dekh lein jo aapko pasand ho iske mutaalliq mujhey bataein mein usey talaaq de doonga . iddat guzarney ke baad aap us se nikah kar lein. is par Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah tumharey ahal aur maal mein barkat ata farmaai tumhara bazar kidhar hai? chunanche maine bani-qainuqaa ka bazar unhein bata diya, jab wahan se kuchh tijarat karke lautey to unke sath kuchh paneer aur ghi tha phir wo isi tarah rozaana subah sawerey bazar mein chaley jatey aur tijarat kartey aakhir aik din khidmate-nabawii mein aaey to unke jism par (khushboo ki) zardi ka nishan tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye kya hai unhon-ne bataya ke maine shadi kar li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mehar kitna ada kya hai? arz kya ke soney ki aik guthli ya (ye kaha ke) aik guthli ke wazan barabar sona ada kya hai, ye shak Ibrahim rawi ko hua."
3781,"jab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) (Makka se hijrat karke Madina aaey to) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke aur Sad-bin-Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan bhai chaara kara diya. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bahut daulat mand they, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Ansar ko malum hai ke main unmein sabse zyada maaldaar hon isliye main apna aadha aadhaa maal apne aur aap ke darmyan baant dena chahta hun aur mere ghar mein 2 beeviyan hain jo aapko pasand ho mein usey talaaq de doonga uski iddat guzar janey par aap us se nikah kar lein. Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah tumharey ahal w maal mein barkat ata farmaaey, (mujh ko apna bazar dikhla do) phir wo bazar se us waqt tak wapas nahi aaey jab tak kuchh ghi aur paneer bataur nafa bacha nahi liya. thodey hi dinon ke baad jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein wo hazir huey to jism par zardi ka nishan tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye kya hai? boley ke maine aik Ansari khatun se shadi kar li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha mehar kya diya hai? boley aik guthli ke barabar sona ya (ye kaha ke) soney ki aik guthli di hai, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya achchha ab walima karo chahe aik bakri hi se ho."
3782,"Ansar ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! khajoor ke baghaat hamarey aur muhajireen ke darmyan taqseem farma dein, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aisa nahi karunga is par Ansar ne (muhaajireen se) kaha phir aap aisa kar lein ke kaam hamari taraf se aap anjam diya karein aur khajooron mein aap hamarey sathi ho jaaein. muhajireen ne kaha ham ne aap logon ki ye baat suni aur ham aisa hi karengey."
3783,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ya yun bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Ansar se sirf momin hi mohabbat rakhega aur unse sirf munafiq hi bughz rakhega. to jo shakhs unse mohabbat karey us se Allah mohabbat karega aur jo unse bughz rakhega us se Allah Taala bughz rakhega (ma'loom hua ke Ansar ki mohabbat eman ki alamat hai aur unse dushmanii rakhna be-iimaan logon ka kaam hai).
3784,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''iimaan ki nishani Ansar se mohabbat rakhna hai aur nifaq ki nishani Ansar se bughz rakhna hai.''
3785,"aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ansaar ki) aurton aur bachchon ko mere guman ke mutabiq kisi shadi se wapas aatey huey dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey aur farmaya Allah ( gawah hai) tum log mujhey sabse zyada azeez ho, teen baar aap ne aisa hi farmaayaa."
3786,Ansar ki aik aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin. unke sath aik unka bachcha bhi tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kalam kya phir farmaya is zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. tum log mujhey sabse zyada mahboob ho 2 martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye jumla farmaayaa.
3787,Ansar ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! har Nabi ke perokar log hotey hain aur ham ne aap ki taabea'daarii ki hai. aap Allah se dua farmaein ke Allah hamarey taabea'daaron ko bhi ham mein Sharik kar de. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski dua farmai. phir maine us hadis ka zikr Abdur-Rehman bin abi Laila ke samney kya to unhon-ne kaha ke Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi ye hadis bayan ki thi.
3788,"Ansar ne arz kya har qaum ke perokar ( haalii mawaalii ( hotey hain, ham to aap ke perokar baney. aap dua farmaein ke Allah Taala hamarey taabea'daaron ko bhi ham mein Sharik kar de. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai ''aey Allah ! unke taabea'daaron ko bhi unhiin mein se kar de.'' Amr ne bayan kya ke phir maine us hadis ka tazkira Abdur-Rehman bin abi Laila se kya to unhon-ne (ta'jjub ke taur par) kaha Zaid ne aisa kahaa? Shoba ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke ye Zaid, Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) hain (na aur koi Zaid jaisey Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) wghaira jaisey ibn-abii-Lailaa ne guman kya)."
3789,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''banu-Najjaar ka gharaana Ansar mein se sabse behtar gharaana hai phir banu-abdul-ash'hal ka, phir banu-al-Haaris bin khazraj ka, phir banu-Saaida bin Kab bin khazraj akbar kaa' jo Aus ka bhai tha, khazraj akbar aur Aus donon Harisa ke betey they aur Ansar ka har gharaana umda hi hai. Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke kai qabeelon ko ham par fazeelat di hai, unse kisi ne kaha tujh ko bhi to bahut se qabeelon par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fazeelat di hai aur Abdus-Samad ne kaha ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne bayan kya : maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unse abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki, is riwayat mein Sad ke bap ka naam Ubada mazkoor hai."
3790,"Ansar mein sabse behtar ya Ansar ke gharaanon mein sabse behtar banu-Najjaar, banu-abdul-Ash'hal, banu-Haaris aur banu-Saaida ke gharaaney hain."
3791,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ansaar ka sabse behtreen gharaana banu-Najjaar ka gharaana hai phir banu-abdul-Ash'hal ka phir banii-Haaris ka, phir banii-Saaida ka aur Ansar ke tamam gharaanon mein khair hai. phir hamari mulaqat Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se hui to wo abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney lagey tumhen malum nahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke behtreen gharaanon ki tareef ki aur hamein (banu-Saaida) ko sabse akheer mein rakha to Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Ansar ke sabse behtreen khandanon ka bayan hua aur ham sabse akheer mein kar diye gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tumharey liye kafi nahi ke tumhara khandan bhi behtreen khandan hai."
3792,"aik Ansari sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! falan shakhs ki tarah mujhey bhi aap Hakim bana dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere baad (duniyaawii maamlaat mein) tum par dusron ko tarjeeh di jaeygi isliye sabr se kaam lenaa, yahan tak ke mujh se hauz par aa milo.''"
3793,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar se farmaya ''mere baad tum dekhogey ke tum par dusron ko fauqiyat di jaeygi, to tum sabr karna yahan tak ke mujh se aa milo aur meri tum se mulaqat hauz par hogii.''"
3794,"jab wo Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khaleefa Waleed bin Abdul-Malik ke yahan janey ke liye nikley. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ko bulaya taake Bahrain ka mulk bataur jaageer unhein ata farma dein. Ansar ne kaha jab tak aap hamarey bhai muhajireen ko bhi usi jaisi jaageer na ata farmaein ham usey qabool nahi karengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''dekho jab aaj tum qabool nahi kartey ho to phir mere baad bhi sabr karna yahan tak ke mujh se aa milo, kyonke mere baad qareeb hi tumhari haq-talfii honey wali hai.''"
3795,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (khandaq khodtey waqt) farmaya ''haqeeqii zindagi to sirf aakhirat ki zindagi hai, to aey Allaah! Ansar aur muhajireen par apna karam farmaa. ''aur Qatada se riwayat hai unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi tarah, aur unhon-ne bayan kya usmein yun hai'' to Ansar ki maghfirat farma de.''"
3796,"aap ne farmaya ke Ansar Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par (khandaq khodtey huey) ye sher padhtey they (نحن الذين بايعوا محمدا على الجهاد ما حيينا أبدا) ''ham wo hain jinhoney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jihad par bait ki hai, jab tak hamari jaan mein jaan hai.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (jab ye suna to ( iske jawab mein yun farmaayaa (اللهم لا عيش إلا عيش الآخره فأكرم الأنصار والمهاجره) ''aey Allaah! aakhirat ki zindagi ke siwa aur koi zindagi haqiqi zindagi nahi hai, to Ansar aur muhajireen par apna Fazal w karam farmaa.''"
3797,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey to ham khandaq khod rahe they aur apne kandhon par mitti utha rahe they. us waqt aap ne ye dua farmaaii (اللهم لا عيش إلا عيش الآخره فاغفر للمهاجرين والأنصار‏) ''aey Allah ! aakhirat ki zindagi ke siwa aur koi zindagi haqiqi zindagi nahi, isliye Ansar aur muhajireen ki to maghfirat farmaa.''"
3798,"aik sahib (khud Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hi murad hain) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhookey hazir huey, aap ne unhein paak beeviyon ke yahan bhejaa. (taake unko khana khilaa dein) paak beeviyon ne kelha bheja ke hamarey paas pani ke siwa aur kuchh nahi hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unki kon mehmani karega? aik Ansari sahabi boley mein karunga. chunanche wo unko apne ghar le gaey aur apni biwi se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mehman ki khaatir tawaazeh kar, biwi ne kaha ke ghar mein bachchon ke khaney ke siwa aur koi cheez bhi nahi hai, unhon-ne kaha jo kuchh bhi hai usey nikal do aur charagh jalaa lo aur bachchey agar khana maangtey hain to unhein sulaa do. biwi ne khana nikal diya aur charagh jalaa diya aur apne bachchon ko (bhookaa) sulaa diya, phir wo dikhaa to ye rahi thin jaisey charagh durust kar rahi hun lekin unhon-ne usey bujhaa diya, iske baad donon miyan biwi mehman par zahir karne lagey ke maano wo bhi unke sath kha rahe hain, lekin un donon ne (apne bachchon samet raat) faaqe se guzaar di, subah ke waqt jab wo sahabi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum donon miyan biwi ke nek amal par raat ko Allah Taala hans padaa ya (ye farmaya ke usey) pasand kya, is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii (ويؤثرون على أنفسهم ولو كان بهم خصاصة ومن يوق شح نفسه فأولئك هم المفلحون‏)''aur wo ( Ansar ( tarjeeh detey hain apne nafson ke uper (doosrey ghareeb sahaba ko) agarche wo khud bhi faaqa hi mein hon aur jo apni tabeeat ke kanjoosii se mehfooz rakha gaya so aisey hi log falaah paaney waley hain.''"
3799,"Abu-Bakar aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Ansar ki aik majlis se guzrey, dekha ke tamam ahale-majlis ro rahe hain, puchha aap log kyon ro rahe hain? majlis walon ne kaha ke abhi ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis ko yad kar rahe they jis mein ham betha kartey they (ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke maut ke marz ka waqia hai) iske baad ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko waaqie ki itlaa di, bayan kya ke is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laaey, sar Mubarak par kapdey ki patti bandhi hui thi, rawi ne bayan kya ke phir aap member par tashrif laey aur uske baad phir kabhi member par aap tashrif na la sakey, aap ne Allah ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya main tumhen Ansar ke barey mein wasiiyat karta hun ke wo mere jism w jaan hain, unhon-ne apni tamam zimmedaariyaan poori ki hain lekin iska badla jo unhein milnaa chahiye tha, wo milnaa abhi baqi hai, isliye tum log bhi unke nek logon ki nekiyon ki qadr karna aur unke khata kaaron se darguzar kartey rehna."
3800,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne donon kandhon par chadar odhey huey they, aur (sar Mubarak par) aik siyah patti (bandhii hui thi) aap member par baith gaey aur Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya : ammaa ba'd, aey logo! dusron ki to bahut kasarat ho jaeygi lekin Ansar kam ho jaeinge aur wo aisey ho jaeinge jaisey khaney mein namak hota hai, to tum mein se jo shakhs bhi kisi aisey mahakme mein Hakim ho jiske zariey kisi ko nuqsan w nafa pahuncha sakta ho to usey Ansar ke nek logon ka istiqbaal karna chahiye aur unke khata kaaron se darguzar karna chahiye"
3801,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Ansar mere jism w jaan hain, aik daur aayega ke doosrey log to bahut ho jaeinge , lekin Ansar kam reh jaeinge , isliye unke nek logon ka isteqbaal karna, aur khata kaaron se darguzar kya karna. ''"
3802,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hadiya mein aik reshamii hulla aaya to sahaba usey chhooney lagey aur uski narmii aur nazaakat par tajjub karne lagey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke tumhen uski narmii par tajjub hai, Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke roomaal ( jannat mein) us se kahin behtar hain ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) us se kahin zyada narm w naazuk hain. is hadis ki riwayat Qatada aur Zohri ne bhi ki hai, unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai."
3803,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut par arsh hil gaya aur Aamash se riwayat hai, unse Abu-Saleh ne bayan kya aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat kya, aik sahib ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Bara (Raziallahu anhu) to is tarah bayan kartey hain ke charpai jis par Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki laash rakhi hui thi, hil gaee thi. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha un donon qabeelon ( Aus aur khazraj (ke darmyan ( zamana jahiliyat mein) dushmanii thi, maine khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai ke Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut par arsh Rehman hil gaya tha."
3804,"aik qaum ( yahood bani Qureza ( ne Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko saalis maan kar hathiyar daal diye to unhein bulaney ke liye aadmi bheja gaya aur wo gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaey. jab us jagah ke qareeb pahunchey jisey (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dinon jang mein) Namaz padhney ke liye muntakhab kya hua tha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke apne sabse behtar shakhs ke liye ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ( apne sardaar ko leney ke liye khadey ho jao. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Sad ! unhon-ne tum ko saalis maan kar hathiyar daal diye hain. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir mera faisla ye hai ke unke jo log jang karne waley hain unhein qatl kar diya jaey aur unki aurton, bachchon ko jangi qaidi bana liya jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum ne Allah ke faisley ke mutabiq faisla kya ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) Farishtey ke hukm ke mutabiq faisla kya hai."
3805,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis se uth kar do sahabi aik andherii raat mein (apne ghar ki taraf ( janey lagey to aik ghaibii noor unke aagey-aagey chal raha tha, phir jab wo juda huey to unke saath-saath wo noor bhi alag alag ho gaya aur Mamar ne Sabit se bayan kya aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik doosrey Ansari sahabi (ke sath ye karaamat pesh aai thi) aur Hammad ne bayan kya, unhein Sabit ne khabar di aur unhein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Usaid-bin-Huzair aur Ibaad-bin-Bishr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ye karaamat pesh aai thi. ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se naql kya hai."
3806,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qur'aan char (sahaaba) Abdullaah-bin-Mas'ood, abu-Huzaifa ke ghulam Salim aur Ubai-bin-Kab aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se seekho.''"
3807,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ansaar ka behtreen gharaana banu-Najjaar ka gharaana hai, phir banu-abdul-Ash'hal kaa, phir banu- Abdul Haris ka, phir banu-Saaida ka aur khair Ansar ke tamam gharaanon mein hai. Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur wo Islam qabool karne mein badi qadaamat rakhtey they ke mera khayal hai, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham par dusron ko fazeelat de di hai, unse kaha gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum ko bhi to bahut se logon par fazeelat di hai) aetraz ki kya baat hai)."
3808,"us waqt se unki mohabbat mere dil mein baith gaee jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna ke Quran char aadmiyon se seekho, Abdullah-bin-Masood se, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhiin ke naam se shuruaat ki, aur abu-Huzaifa ke ghulam Salim se, Muaz-bin-Jabal se aur Ubai-bin-Kab se."
3809,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ubai-bin-Kab se farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tum ko sura ( لم يكن الذين كفروا‏ ( sunaun. Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) boley kya Allah Taala ne mera naam liya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, is par Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) khushi ke maarey roney lagey."
3810,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein char aadmi jin sab ka talluq qabila Ansar se tha, Quran Majeed jama karne waley they. Uabii-bin-Ka'b, Muaaz-bin-Jabal, Abu-Zaid aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) maine puchha : Abu-Zaid kon hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke wo mere aik chacha hain."
3811,"Uhud ki ladai ke mauqe par jab sahaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb se idhar-udhar chalney lagey to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt apni aik dhaal se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hifazat kar rahe they. abu-Talha badey teerandaaz they aur khub kheench kar teer chalaayaa kartey they chunanche us din 2 ya 3 kamaanein unhon-ne tod di thin. us waqt agar koi musalman tarkash liye huey guzarta to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke iske teer abu-Talha ko de do. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) halaat malum karne ke liye uchak kar dekhney lagtey to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) arz kartey : ya Nabi Allah ! aap par mere maan-baap qurbaan hon, uchak kar n dekhein, kahin koi teer aapko na lag jaey. mera Sina Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke seeney ki dhaal bana raha aur maine Aaisha binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) (abu-Talha ki beewii) ko dekha ke apna izaar uthaey huey (ghaaziyon ki madad mein) badi tezi ke sath mashghool thin. (is khidmat mein unke inhimaak w istighraaq ki wjah se unhein kapdon tak ka hosh na tha yahan tak ke) mein unki pindliyon ke zewar dekh sakta tha. intihai jaldi ke sath mishkeezey apni peethon par liye jati thin aur musalmanon ko pilaa kar wapas aati thin aur phir unhein bhar kar ley jaatiin aur unka pani musalmanon ko pilaatiin aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath se us din 2 ya teen martaba talwaar chhoot kar gir padi thi."
3812,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur kisi ke mutaalliq ye nahi suna ke wo ahle-jannat mein se hain, bayan kya ke aayat وشهد شاهد من بني إسرائيل (sura Ahqaaf: 10 ( unhiin ke barey mein nazil hui thi ( rawi hadis Abdullah-bin Yusuf ne) bayan kya ke aayat ke nuzool ke mutaalliq Malik ka qaul hai ya hadis mein isi tarah tha."
3813,"main masjide-Nabawi mein betha hua tha ke aik buzurg masjid mein dakhil huey jinke chehrey par khushoo w khuzooa' ke aasaar zahir they logon ne kaha ke ye buzurg jannati logon mein se hain, phir unhon-ne 2 rakaat Namaz mukhtasar tareeqe par padhi aur bahar nikal gaey main bhi unke peechhey ho liya aur arz kya ke jab aap masjid mein dakhil huey they, to logon ne kaha ke ye buzurg jannat walon mein se hain, is par unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! kisi ke liye aisi baat zaban se nikaalnaa munasib nahi hai jisey wo na janta ho aur main tumhen bataaoonga ke aisa kyon hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein, maine aik khuwab dekha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usey bayan kya maine khuwab ye dekha tha ke jaisey mein aik baagh mein hun, phir unhon-ne uski wusat aur uske sabza zaaron ka zikr kya us baagh ke darmyan mein aik lohey ka sutoon hai jiska nichlaa hissey zameen mein hai aur uper ka aasman par aur uski choti par aik ghanaa darakht hai) العروة ( mujh se kaha gaya ke is par chadh jao maine kaha ke mujh main to itni taqat nahi hai itney mein aik khaadim aaya aur peechhey se mere kapdey us ne uthaey to main chadh gaya aur jab main uski choti par pahunch gaya to maine us ghaney darakht ko pakad liya mujh se kaha gaya ke us darakht ko poori mazbootii ke sath pakad ley , abhi main usey apne hath se pakdey huey tha ke meri aankh khul gaee. ye khuwab jab maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo baagh tum ne dekha hai, wo to Islam hai aur is mein sutoon Islam ka sutoon hai aur) العروة ( ) ghanaa darakht ( ) عروة الوثقى ( hai isliye tum Islam par martey dam tak qaaim rahogey. ye buzurg Abdullaah-bin-Salaam they aur mujh se khaleefa ne bayan kya unse Muaz ne bayan kya unse ibn-A'un ne bayan kya unse Muhammad ne unse Qais-bin-Ibaad ne bayan kya Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne ( munsif .) ( khaadim (ke bajaey ( وصيف (ka lafz zikr kya."
3814,"main Madina Munawra hazir hua to maine Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki, unhon-ne kaha, aao tumhen main sattu aur khajoor khilaaunga aur tum aik (baa-azmat) makan mein dakhil hogey (ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi usmein tashrif le gaey they) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumhara qiyam aik aisey mulk mein hai jahan soodii maamlaat bahut aam hain agar tumhara kisi shakhs par koi haq ho aur phir wo tumhen aik tinkey ya jau ke aik daney ya aik ghaas ke barabar bhi hadiya de to usey qabool na karna kyonke wo bhi sood hai. nazar, Abu-Dawud aur Wahab ne (apni riwayaton mein) (البيت‏) ( ghar (ka zikr nahi kya."
3815,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap ne farmaya (doosri sanad) aur mujh se sadqa ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Abda ne khabar di, unhein Hisham ne unse unke walid ne bayan kya ke maine Abdullaah-bin-Ja'far se suna unhon-ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(apne zamaney mein) Maryam (Alaihissalam) sabse afzal aurat thin aur (is ummat mein) Khadija (Raziallahu anha) sabse afzal hain.''"
3816,"Hisham ne mere paas apne walid ( Urwa ( se likh kar bheja ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kisi biwi ke maamle mein, maine itni ghairat nahi mehsus ki jitni ghairat Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke maamle mein mehsus karti thi wo mere nikah se pahley hi wafat pa chuki thin lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se main unka zikr suntii rehti thi aur Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya tha ke unhein (jannat mein) mautaa ke mahal ki khushkhabri suna dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) agar kabhi bakri zabah kartey to unse meil-muhabbat rakhney wali khawaateen ko usmein se itna hadiya bhejtey jo unke liye kafi ho jata."
3817,"Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke maamle mein, main jitni ghairat mehsus karti thi utni kisi aurat ke mamley mein nahi, kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unka zikr aksar kya kartey they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mera nikah unki wafat ke teen saal baad hua tha aur Allah Taala ne unhein hukm diya tha ya Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ke zariey ye paigham pahunchaya tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein jannat mein motiyon ke aik mahal ki bashaarat de dein."
3818,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tamam beeviyon mein jitni ghairat mujhey Khadija (Raziallahu anha) se aati thi itni kisi aur se nahi aati thi halanke unhein maine dekha bhi nahi tha, lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unka zikr kasrat se farmaya kartey they aur agar koi bakri zabah kartey to iske tukdey tukdey karke Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ki milney waaliyon ko bhejtey they. maine aksar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha jaisey duniya mein Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke siwa koi aurat hai hi nahin! is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke wo aisi thin aur aisi thin aur unse mere aulad hai."
3819,"maine Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii se puchha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ko bashaarat di thi? unhon-ne farmaya ke haan, jannat mein motiyon ke aik mahal ki bashaarat di thi, jahan na koi shor-ghul hoga aur na thakan hogi."
3820,Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha ya Rasulullah! Khadija (Raziallahu anha) aap ke paas aik bartan liye aa rahi hain jis mein saalan ya ( farmaya ( khana ya ( farmaya ( peeney ki cheez hai jab wo aap ke paas aaiin to unke rab ki taraf se unhein salam pahuncha diijiyega aur meri taraf se bhi! aur unhein jannat mein motiyon ke aik mahal ki bashaarat de diijiyega jahan na shor w hangaama hoga aur na takleef w thakan hogi.
3821,"Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ki behan haala binte- khuwelid ne aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se andar aaney ki ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ki ijazat leney ki ada yad aa gaee, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaunk uthey aur farmaya ''Allaah! ye to haala hain'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke mujhey is par badi ghairat aai , maine kaha aap Quraish ki kis boodhi ka zikr kya kartey hain jiske masoodon par bhi daanton ke toot janey ki wjah se ( sirf surkhi baqi reh gaee thi) aur jisey marey huey bhi aik zamana guzar chuka hai, Allah Taala ne aapko us se behtar biwi de di hai."
3822,Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya jab se main Islam mein dakhil hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ( ghar ke andar aaney se) nahi rokaa (jab bhi maine ijazat chahi (aur jab bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey dekhtey to muskuraatey.
3823,"zamana jahiliyat mein '' zul-khalasa '' naam ke aik but kada tha usey ( الكعبة اليمانية (ya ( الكعبة الشأمية ( bhi kehtey they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ''zul-khalasa"" ke wujood se main jis takleef mein mubtala hun, kya tum mujhey us se nijat dila saktey ho?'' unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir qabila Ahmas ke dedh so sawaaron ko main lekar chalaa, unhon-ne bayan kya aur ham ne but-kadey ko dhaa diya aur is mein jo they unko qatl kar diya, phir ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di to aap ne hamarey liye aur qabila Ahmas ke liye dua farmai."
3824,Uhud ki ladai mein jab mushrekeen haar chukey to iblees ne chilla kar kaha : aey Allah ke bando! peechhey walon ko) qatl karo) chunanche aagey ke musalman peechhey walon par pil padey aur unhein qatl karna shuru kar diya. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo dekha to unke walid ( Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi wahin maujood they unhon-ne pukar kar kaha : aey Allah ke bandon ye to mere walid hain mere walid ! Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya : Allah ki qism ! us waqt tak log wahan se nahi hatey jab tak unhein qatl na kar liya. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne sirf itna kaha Allah tumhari maghfirat kare. (Hishaam ne bayan kya ke) Allah ki qasam! Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) barabar ye kalima dua'aiya kehtey rahe (ke Allah unke walid par hamla karne walon ko bakhshney jo ke mahz ghalatfahmii ki wjah se ye harkat kar baithey) ye dua martey dam tak kartey rahe.
3825,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya : Hind-bint-Utba (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Islam laney ke baad) hazir huin aur kehney lagiin ya Rasulullah! poori zameen par kisi gharaaney ki zillat aap ke gharaaney ki zillat si zyada mere liye khushi ka baais nahi thi lekin aaj kisi gharaaney ki izzat poori zameen par aap ke gharaaney ki izzat se zyada mere liye khushi ki wjah nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ismein abhi aur taraqqi hogi. us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai'' phir Hind ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! Abu-Sufiyan bahut kanjoos hain to kya usmein kuchh harj hai agar main unke maal mein se (unki ijazat ke baghair) baal-bachchon ko khilaa diya aur pilaa diya karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya haan lekin main samajhta hun ke ye dastoor ke mutabiq hona chahiye
3826,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) se ( wadi ( baldah ke nichley ilaqe mein mulaqat hui, ye qissa nuzoole-wahi se pahley ka hai, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik dastar-khuwaan bichhaayaa gaya to Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail ne khaney se inkar kar diya aur jin logon ne dastar-khuwaan bichhaayaa tha unse kaha ke apne buton ke naam par jo tum zabiha kartey ho mein usey nahi khata main to bas wahi zabiha khaya karta hun jis par sirf Allah ka naam liya gaya ho, Zaid-bin-Amr Quraish par unke zabeehey ke barey mein aib lagaya kartey aur kehtey they ke bakri ko paida to kya Allah Taala ne, usi ne uske liye aasman se pani barsaya hai usi ne uske liye zameen se ghaas ugaaii , phir tum log Allah ke siwa doosrey (buton ke) naamon par usey zabah kartey ho. Zaid ne ye kalimaat unke un kaamon par aetraz kartey huey aur unke us amal ko bahut badi ghalati qarar detey huey kahey they."
3827,"Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail Sham (Syria) gaey, Deen ( khalis ( ki talash mein nikley. wahan wo aik Yahudi aalim se miley to unhon-ne unke Deen ke barey mein puchha aur kaha mumkin hai ke main tumhara Deen ikhtiyar kar loon isliye tum mujhey apne Deen ke mutaalliq bataao. Yahudi aalim ne kaha ke hamarey Deen main tum us waqt tak dakhil nahi ho saktey jab tak tum Allah ke ghazab ke aik hisse ke liye taiyaar na ho jao, is par Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke waah! main Allah ke ghazab hi se bhag kar aaya hun, phir Allah ke ghazab ko main apne uper kabhi na loonga aur na mujh ko usey uthaney ki taqat hai ! kya tum mujhey kisi aur doosrey Deen ka kuchh pata bata saktey ho? us aalim ne kaha, main nahi janta (koii Deen sachcha ho to Deen Hanif ho). Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha deene-haneef kya hai? us aalim ne kaha ke Ibrahim ka deen, jo na Yahudi they aur na nasrani aur wo Allah ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nahi kartey they. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) wahan se chaley aaey aur aik nasrani paadrii se miley, unse bhi apna khayal bayan kya usne bhi yahi kaha ke tum hamarey Deen mein aaogey to Allah Taala ki laanat mein se aik hissey logey. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main Allah ki laanat se hi bachney ke liye to ye sab kuchh kar raha hun Allah ki laanat uthaney ki mujh mein taqat nahi aur na main iska ye ghazab kis tarah utha sakta hun ! kya tum mere liye iske siwa koi aur Deen batla saktey ho? paadrii ne kaha ke meri nazar mein ho to sirf aik deene-haneef sachcha Deen hai. Zaid ne puchha deene-haneef kya hai? kaha ke wo deene-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) hai jo na Yahudi they aur na nasrani aur Allah ke siwa wo kisi ki puja nahi kartey they. Zaid ne jab deene-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ke barey mein unki ye raey suni to wahan se rawaana ho gaey aur us sar zameen se bahar nikal kar apne donon hath aasman ki taraf uthaey aur ye dua ki اللهم إني أشهد أني على دين إبراهيمaey Allaah! mein gawahi deta hun ke main deene-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) par hun."
3828,"maine Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail ko Kaba se apni peeth lagaey huey khadey ho kar ye kehtey suna, aey Quraish ke logo ! Allah ki qism mere siwa aur koi tumharey yahan deene-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) par nahi hai aur Zaid betiyon ko zinda nahi gaadtey they aur aisey shakhs se jo apni beti ko mar daalnaa chahta kehtey uski jaan na ley iske tamam kharchon ka zimma main leta hun, chunanche ladki ko apni parwarish mein rakh letey jab wo badi ho jati to uske bap se kehtey ab agar tum chaho to main tumhari ladki ko tumharey hawale kar sakta hun aur agar tumhari marzii ho to main iske sab kaam poorey kar doonga."
3829,jab Kaba ki tameer ho rahi thi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) uske liye patthar dho rahe they Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha apna tehband gardan par rakh lein is tarah patthar ki (kharaash lagney se) bach jaengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab aisa kya to aap zameen par gir padey aur aap ki nazar aasman par gad gaee jab hosh hua to aap ne chacha se farmaya ke mera tehband laaein phir unhon-ne aap ka tehband khub mazbut baandh diya.
3830,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein Baitullah ke gird ihaatey ki diwar na thi log Kaba ke gird Namaz padhtey they phir jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya to unhon-ne iske gird diwar banwai. Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke ye diwarein bhi past thin Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko buland kya.
3831,Aashoora ka roza Quraish ke log zamana-e-jahiliyat mein rakhtey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi usey baqi rakha tha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud bhi us din roza rakha aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi roza rakhney ka hukm diya lekin jab Ramazan ka roza 2 hijri mein farz hua to iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke jiska ji chahey Aashoora ka roza rakhey aur jo na chahey na rakhey .
3832,zamana jahiliyat mein log Haj ke mahinon mein Umra karna bahut bada gunah khayal kartey they. wo Mohrim ko safar kehtey. unke yahan ye kahawat thi ke oont ki peeth ka zakhm jab achchha honey lagey aur) haajiyon ke) qadamon ke nishanat mit chukein to ab Umra karne walon ka Umra jaaiz hua. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ashaab ke sath Zil-Hijja ki chothi taareekh ko Haj ka ehram baandhey huey (Makka) tashrif laey to aap ne sahaba ko hukm diya ke apne Haj ko Umra kar daalein ( tawaaf aur saee karke ehram khol dein). sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! (is Umra aur Haj ke doran mein) kya cheezein halal hongii? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tamam cheezein! jo ehram ke na honey ki haalat mein halal thin wo sab halal ho jaaeingii.
3833,zamana jahiliyat mein aik martaba sailaab aaya ke (Makka ki) donon pahaadiyon ke darmyan pani hi pani ho gaya. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke bayan kartey they ke is hadis ka aik bahut bada qissa hai.
3834,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) qabila Ahmas ki aik aurat se miley unka naam Zenab binte- muhajir tha. aap ne dekha ke wo baat hi nahi kartin. malum farmaya kya baat hai ye baat kyon nahi kartiin? logon ne bataya ke mukammal khamoshi ke sath Haj karne ki mannat maana hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse farmaya : ajii baat karo is tarah Haj karna to jahiliyat ki rasm hai, chunanche us ne baat ki aur puchha aap kon hain? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main muhajireen ka aik aadmi hun. unhon-ne puchha ke muhajireen ke kis qabeele se hain? aap ne farmaya ke Quraish se, unhon-ne puchha Quraish ke kis khandan se ? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par farmaya tum bahut poochhney wali aurat ho, mein Abu-Bakar hun. iske baad unhon-ne puchha jahiliyat ke baad Allah Taala ne jo hamein ye Deen haq ata farmaya hai is par ham ( musalman ( Kab tak qaaim reh sakengey ? aap ne farmaya is par tumhara qiyam us waqt tak rahega jab tak tumharey imam Hakim seedhey rahengey. us khatun ne puchha imam se kya murad hai? aap ne farmaya : kya tumhari qaum mein sardaar aur ashraaf log nahi hain jo agar logon ko koi hukm dein to wo uski itaat karein? usne kaha ke kyon nahi hain. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke imam se yahi murad hain."
3835,"aik kali aurat jo kisi Arab ki baandi thi Islam laai aur masjid mein uske rehney ke liye aik kothrii thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya wo hamarey yahan aaya karti aur baatein kya karti thi, lekin jab baton se farigh ho jati to wo ye sher padhtii ''aur haar wala din bhi hamarey rab ke Ajaaib qudrat mein se hai, ke usi ne (apne fazl sey) kufr ke Shahar se mujhey chhudaayaa.''us ne jab kai martaba ye sher padha to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne us se malum kya ke haar waley din ka qissa kya hai? us ne bayan kya ke mere maalikon ke gharaaney ki aik ladki (jo nai dulhan thi) laal chamdey ka aik haar baandhey huey thi. wo bahar nikli to ittifaq se wo gir gaya. aik cheel ki is par nazar padi aur wo usey gosht samajh kar utha ley gaee. logon ne mujh par uski chori ki tohmat lagai aur mujhey sazaaein deeni shuru kin. yahan tak ke meri sharmgah ki bhi talashi li. khair wo abhi mere charon taraf jama hi they aur main apni museebat mein mubtala thi ke cheel aai aur hamarey saron ke bilkul uper udney lagi phir us ne wahi haar nichey gira diya. logon ne usey utha liya to maine unse kaha isi ke liye tum log mujhey ittihaam laga rahe they halanke main be-gunaah thi."
3836,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''haan! agar kisi ko qism khaani hi ho to Allah ke siwa aur kisi ki qism na khaaey.''
3837,unke walid Qasim-bin-Muhammad janaaze ke aagey-aagey chala kartey they aur janaaza ko dekh kar khadey nahi hotey they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hawale se wo bayan kartey they ke zamane jahiliyat mein log janaaze ke liye khadey ho jaya kartey they aur usey dekh kar do baar kehtey they ke aey marney waley jis tarah apni zindagi main to apne ghar walon ke sath tha ab waise hi kisi parindey ke bhes mein hai.
3838,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jab tak dhoop sabeer pahaadii par na aa jati Quraish (Haj mein) Muzdalfa se nahi nikla kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki mukhalifat ki aur suraj nikalney se pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan se kooch kya.
3839,iske (ma'na ٰhain) bharaa hua piyala jiska musalsal daur chaley.
3840,maine apne walid se suna wo kehtey they ke zamana-e-jahiliyat mein (ye lafz istemal kartey they) (اسقنا كأسا دهاقا‏) yaanii ham ko bharpur jaame-sharaab pilaatey raho.
3841,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse sachchii baat jo koi shaair keh sakta tha wo Labid shaair ne kahii'' haan Allah ke siwa har cheez baatil hai.aur Umayya bin abi Salat (jaahiliyat ka aik shaair ( musalman honey ke qareeb tha.
3842,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ghulam tha jo rozaana unhein kuchh kamaaii diya karta tha aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) usey apni zarurat mein istemal kya kartey they. aik din wo ghulam koi cheez laya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi usmein se kha liya. phir ghulam ne kaha aapko malum hai? ye kaisi kamaaii se hai? aap ne malum farmaya kaisi hai? usne kaha maine zamana jahiliyat mein aik shakhs ke liye kahaanat ki thi halanke mujhey kahaanat nahi aati thi, maine usey sirf dhoka diya tha lekin ittifaq se wo mujhey mil gaya aur us ne uski ujrat mein mujh ko ye cheez di thi, aap kha bhi chukey hain. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye suntey hi apna hath munh mein daala aur pet ki tamam cheezein qai karke nikal daaliin."
3843,"zamana jahiliyat ke log ( Hablil-Habla ( tak qeemat ki adaaeygi ke wa'de par, oont ka gosht udhaar bechaa kartey they. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke (Hablil-Habla) ka matlab ye hai ke koi haamla ontni apna bachcha janey phir wo nau-zaayeda bachcha (badh kar) haamla ho, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah ki khareed-farokht ko naajaaiz qarar diya tha."
3844,"ham Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey they. wo ham se Ansar ke mutaalliq bayan farmaya kartey they aur mujh se farmatey ke tumhari qaum ne falan mauqe par ye kaarnaama anjam diya, falan mauqe par ye kaarnaama anjam diya."
3845,"jahiliyat mein sabse pahlaa qasaama hamarey hi qabila banu-Haashim mein hua tha, banu-Haashim ke aik shakhs Amr bin Alqama ko Quraish ke kisi doosrey khandan ke aik shakhs (Khaddaash-bin-abdullaah-Aamirii) ne naukrii par rakhaa, ab ye Haashmii naukar apne sahib ke sath iske oont lekar Sham (Syria) ki taraf chala wahan kahin us naukar ke paas se aik doosra Haashmii shakhs guzraa, uski borii ka bandhan toot gaya tha. us ne apne naukar bhai se iltijaa ki meri madad kar oont baandhney ki mujhey aik rassii dedey. mein us se apna thailaa baandhon. agar rassii na hogi to wo bhag thodey jaeyga us ne aik rassii usey de di aur us ne apni borii ka munh us se baandh liya (aur chala gayaa). phir jab us naukar aur sahib ne aik manzil par padao kya to tamam oont baandhey gaey lekin aik oont khula raha. jis sahib ne haashmii ko naukrii par apne sath rakha tha us ne puchha sab oont to baandhey, ye oont kyon nahi baandha gaya kya baat hai? naukar ne kaha uski rassii maujood nahi hai. sahib ne puchha kya hua uski rassii? aur ghusse mein aa kar aik lakdi is par phenk maari uski maut aan pahunchii. uske (marney se pahley) wahan se aik yamnii shakhs guzar raha tha. Haashmii naukar ne puchha kya Haj ke liye har saal tum Makka jatey ho? usne kaha abhi to irada nahi hai lekin main kabhi jata rehta hun. us naukar ne kaha jab bhi tum Makka pahuncho kya mera aik paigham pahuncha doge? usne kaha haan pahuncha doonga. us naukar ne kaha ke jab bhi tum Haj ke liye jao to pukaarnaa : aey Quraish ke logo! jab wo tumharey paas jama ho jayen to pukaarnaa : aey bani haashim! jab wo tumharey paas aa jayen to unse abu-Taalib poochhna aur unhein batlaanaa ke falan shakhs ne mujhey aik rassii ke liye qatl kar diya. us wasiiyat ke baad wo naukar mar gaya, phir jab iska sahib Makka aaya to abu-Taalib ke yahan bhi gaya. janab abu-Taalib ne malum kya hamarey qabeele ke jis shakhs ko tum apne sath naukrii ke liye le gaey they uska kya hua? usne kaha ke wo bimar ho gaya tha maine khidmat karne mein koi kasar nahi utha rakhi (lekin wo mar gaya to) maine usey dafn kar diya. abu-Taalib ne kaha ke uske liye tumhari taraf se yahi hona chahiye tha. aik muddat ke baad wahi yamnii shakhs jisey Haashmii naukar ne paigham pahunchaney ki wasiiyat ki thi, mausame-Haj mein aaya aur awaz di : aey Quraish ke logo! logon ne bata diya ke yahan hain Quraish. us ne awaz di, aey banu-Haashim! logon ne bataya ke banu-Haashim ye hain. us ne puchha abu-Taalib kahan hain? logon ne bataya to usne kaha ke falan shakhs ne mujhey aik paigham pahunchaney ke liye kaha tha ke falan shakhs ne usey aik rassii ki wjah se qatl kar diya hai. ab janab abu-Taalib us sahib ke yahan aaey aur kaha ke un teen chizon mein se koi cheez pasand kar lo agar tum chaho to so oont diyat mein de do kyonke tum ne hamarey qabeele ke aadmi ko qatl kya hai aur agar chaho to tumhari qaum ke pachaas aadmi uski qism kha lein ke tum ne usey qatl nahi kya. agar tum is par taiyaar nahi to ham tumhen iske badley mein qatl kar dengey. wo shakhs apni qaum ke paas aaya to wo uske liye taiyaar ho gaey ke ham qism kha lengey. phir banu-Haashim ki aik aurat abu-Taalib ke paas aai jo usi qabeele ke aik shakhs se biyaahii hui thi aur apne us shauhar se uska bachcha bhi tha. usne kaha : aey abu-Taalib ! aap meherbani karein aur mere us ladkey ko un pachaas aadmiyon mein maaf kar dein aur jahan qasmein li jati hain (yani rukn aur maqaame-Ibraaheem ke darmyaan) us se wahan qism na lein. abu-Taalib ne usey maaf kar diya. iske baad unmein ka aik aur shakhs aaya aur kaha : aey abu-Taalib ! aap ne so oonton ki jagah pachaas aadmiyon se qism talab ki hai, is tarah har shakhs par 2-2 oont padtey hain. ye 2 oont meri taraf se aap qabool kar lein aur mujhey us maqam par qism khaney ke liye majbur na karein jahan qism li jati hai. abu-Taalib ne usey bhi manzoor kar liya. iske baad Baqiiya jo adtaalees aadmi aaey aur unhon-ne qism khaaii. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is zaat ki qism ! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai abhi us waqia ko pura saal bhi nahi guzra tha ke un adtaalees aadmiyon mein se aik bhi aisa nahi raha jo aankh hilaataa."
3846,"Buaas ki ladai Allah Taala ne (maslihat ki wjah se) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pahley barpa kara di thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laey to yahan Ansar ki jamat mein phoot padi hui thi. unke sardaar maarey ja chukey they ya zakhmi ho chukey they, Allah Taala ne us ladai ko isliye pahley barpa kya tha ke Ansar Islam mein dakhil ho jaaein."
3847,Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya Safa aur Marwa ke darmyan naley ke andar zor se daudnaa sunnat nahi hai yahan jahiliyat ke daur mein log tezi ke sath douda kartey they aur kehtey they ke ham to us pathreelii jagah se daud hi kar paar hongey.
3848,"maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne kaha : aey logo! meri baatein suno ke main tum se bayan karta hun aur (jo kuchh tum ne samjha hai) wo mujhey sunao. aisa na ho ke tum log yahan se uth kar (baghair samjhey) chaley jao aur phir kehney lago ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne yun kaha aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne yun kaha. jo shakhs bhi Baitullah ka tawaaf karey to wo Hateem ke peechhey se tawaaf karey aur hijr ko Hateem na kaha karo ye jahiliyat ka naam hai us waqt logon mein jab koi kisi baat ki qism khata to apna kodaa, jootaa ya kamaan wahan phenk detaa."
3849,maine zamana-e-jahiliyat mein aik bandariyaa dekhi uske charon taraf bahut se bandar jama ho gaey they us bandariyaa ne zina karaya tha isliye sabhon ne mil kar usey rajm (sangsaar) kya aur unke sath main bhi patthar maarney mein Sharik hua.
3850,"jahiliyat ki aadaton mein se ye aadatein hain. nasb ke maamle mein ta'na maarnaa, maiyat par nauha karnaa, teesri aadat ke mutaalliq (Ubaidullaah raawii) bhool gaey they aur Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke log kehtey hain ke wo teesri baat sitaron ko barish ki illat samajhnaa hai."
3851,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki umr chalis (40) saal ki hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hui. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 13 saal Makka Mukarrama mein rahe phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hijrat ka hukm hua aur aap Madina Munawra hijrat karke chaley gaey. wahan das saal rahe phir aap ne wafat farmai is hisab se aap ki kal umr sharif 63 saal hoti hai aur yahi sahi hai.
3852,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke saaey taley chadar par tek lagaey baithey they. ham log mushrekeen se intihai takaaleef utha rahe they. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala se aap dua kyon nahi farmaatey? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) seedhey baith gaey. chehra Mubarak ghusse se surkh ho gaya aur farmaya tum se pahley aisey log guzar chukey hain ke lohey ke kanghon ko unke gosht aur putthon se guzaar kar unki haddiyon tak pahuncha diya gaya aur ye mamla bhi unhein unke Deen se na pher sakaa, kisi ke sar par aaraa rakh kar uske 2 tukdey kar diye gaey aur ye bhi unhein unke Deen se na pher sakaa, is Deen Islam ko to Allah Taala khud hi aik din tamam w kamaal tak pahunchaaeyga ke aik sawar san'aa se hazare-maut tak ( tanha ( jaeyga aur) rastey ( mein usey Allah ke siwa aur kisi ka khof tak na hoga. bayan ne apni riwayat mein ye zyada kya ke '' siwaey bhediye ke, ke us se apni bakriyon ke maamle mein usey dar hoga.''"
3853,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura Najm padhi aur sajda kya us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tamam logon ne sajda kya sirf aik shakhs ko maine dekha ke apne hath mein us ne kankariyaan utha kar is par apna sar rakh diya aur kehney laga ke mere liye bas itna hi kafi hai. maine phir usey dekha ke kufr ki haalat mein wo qatl kya gaya.
3854,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (namaz padhtey huey) sajda ki haalat mein they, Quraish ke kuchh log wahin ird-gird maujood they. itney mein Aqba bin abi mueet oont ki ojhdii bachcha daan laya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peeth Mubarak par usey daal diya. uski wjah se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna sar nahi uthaya phir Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aaein aur gandagi ko peeth Mubarak se hataya aur jisne aisa kya tha usey baddua dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi unke haq mein baddua ki ke aey Allah ! Quraish ki us jamat ko pakad ley. abu-Jahal bin Hisham , Utba-bin- Rabee , Sheba bin Rabee aur Umayya-bin-Khalaf ya ( Umayya ke bajaey aap ne baddua ( Ubai-bin Khalaf (ke haq mein farmai ( shuba rawi hadis Shoba ko tha. Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir maine dekha ke badr ki ladai mein ye sab log qatl kar diye gaey aur aik kuwein mein unhein daal diya gaya tha siwaey Umayya ya abi ke ke iska har aik jod alag alag ho gaya tha isliye kuwein mein nahi daala ja saka."
3855,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se un donon aayaton ke mutaalliq poochho ke unmein mutaabiqat kis tarah paida ki jaey (eik aayat (ولا تقتلوا النفس التي حرم الله) aur dusri aayat ( ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا‏ ( hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se maine puchha to unhon-ne batlaya ke jab sura furqan ki aayat nazil hui to mushrekeene-Makka ne kaha ham ne to un jaanon ka bhi khoon kya hai jinke qatl ko Allah Taala ne haram qarar diya tha ham Allah ke siwa doosrey ma'boodon ki ibadat bhi kartey rahe hain aur badkaariyaan bhi ham ne ki hain. is par Allah Taala ne aayat nazil farmai ( إلا من تاب وآمن‏ ( ''wo log us hukm se alag hain jo tauba kar lein aur eman ley aaein'' to ye aayat unke haq mein nahi hai lekin sura Nisa ki aayat us shakhs ke barey mein hai jo Islam aur Islaami shareeat ke ehkaam jaan kar bhi kisi ko qatl karey to uski saza jahannam hai. maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke us irshad ka zikr Mujahid se kya to unhon-ne kaha ke wo log us hukm se alag hain jo tauba kar lein.
3856,"mujhey mushrekeen ke sabse sakht zulm ke mutaalliq bataao jo mushrekeen ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hateem mein Namaz padh rahe they ke Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet aaya aur zaalim apna kapda Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki gardan Mubarak mein phansaa kar zor se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka gala ghontney laga itney mein Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur unhon-ne us bad-bakht ka kandhaa pakad kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se usey hata diya aur kaha ke tum log aik shakhs ko sirf isliye mar daalnaa chahtey ho ke wo kehta hai ke mera rab Allah hai. Ayaash-bin-Waleed ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) ibne- Ishaq ne ki (aur bayan kya ke) mujh se Yahya bin Urwa ne bayan kya aur unse Urwa ne ke maine Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha aur Abda ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne, unse unke walid ne ke Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya aur Muhammad-bin Amr ne bayan kya, unse abu-Salma ne, usmein yun hai ke mujh se Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya."
3857,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us haalat mein bhi dekha hai jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath panch ghulaam, 2 aurton aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur koi ( musalman ( nahi tha."
3858,jis din mein Islam laya hon doosrey log bhi isi din Islam laey aur Islam mein dakhil hone-waale teesrey aadmi ki haisiyat se mujh par saat (7) din guzrey.
3859,maine Masruq se puchha ke jis raat main jinon ne Quran Majeed suna tha uski khabar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kis ne di thi? Masruq ne kaha ke mujh se tumharey walid Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jinon ki khabar aik babool ke darakht ne di thi.
3860,wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu aur qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye (paanii ka ( aik bartan liye huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey-peechhey chal rahe they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye kon sahib hain? bataya ke main Abu-Hurera hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke istinjey ke liye chand patthar talash kar lao aur haan haddi aur leed na laanaa. to main patthar lekar hazir hua. mein unhein apne kapdey mein rakhey huey tha aur la kar maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb usey rakh diya aur wahan se wapas chala aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat se farigh ho gaey to main phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur maine arz kya ke haddi aur gobar mein kya baat hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isliye ke wo jinon ki khuraak hain. mere paas Naseebeen ke jinon ka aik wafad aaya tha aur kya hi achchhey wo jin they. to unhon-ne mujh se khane-pine ka saman maanga maine unke liye Allah se ye dua ki ke jab bhi haddi ya gobar par unki nazar padey to unke liye us cheez se khana miley.
3861,"jab Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nabwooat ke barey mein malum hua to unhon-ne apne bhai Unais se kaha Makka janey ke liye sawari taiyaar kar aur us shakhs ke mutaalliq jo Nabi honey ka muddaii hai aur kehta hai ke uske paas aasman se khabar aati hai. mere liye khabrein hasil karke laa. uski baton ko khud ghaur se sunnaa aur phir mere paas aanaa. unke bhai wahan se chaley aur Makka hazir ho kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baatein khud suniin phir wapas ho kar unhon-ne Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya ke maine unhein khud dekha hai, wo achchhey akhlaq ka logon ko hukm kartey hain aur maine unse jo kalam suna wo sher nahi hai. is par Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jis maqsad ke liye maine tumhen bheja tha mujhey is par poori tarah tasalli nahi hui, aakhir unhon-ne khud khane-pine ka saman baandhaa, pani se bharaa hua aik puraanaa mishkeeza sath liya aur Makka aaey, masjide-Haraam mein haziri di aur yahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko talash kya. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pehchantey nahi they aur kisi se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mutaalliq poochhna bhi munasib nahi samjha , kuchh raat guzar gaee ke wo letey huey they. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko us haalat mein dekha aur samajh gaey ke koi musaafir hai. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke aap mere ghar par chal kar aaraam keejiye. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) unke peechhey peechhey chaley gaey lekin kisi ne aik doosrey ke barey mein baat nahi ki. jab subah hui to Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna mishkeeza aur khane-pine ka saman uthaya aur masjide-Haraam mein aa gaey. ye din bhi yoonhii guzar gaya aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na dekh sakey. Sham hui to soney ki taiyaarii karne lagey. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) phir wahan se guzrey aur samajh gaey ke abhi apne thikaaney janey ka waqt us shakhs par nahi aaya, wo unhein wahan se phir apne sath ley aaey aur aaj bhi kisi ne aik doosrey se baat cheet nahi ki, tesraa din jab hua aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke sath yahi kaam kya aur apne sath le gaey to unse puchha kya tum mujhey bata saktey ho ke yahan aaney ki wajah kya hai? Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tum mujh se pukhta wada kar lo ke meri rehnumai karogey to main tum ko sab kuchh bata doonga. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne wada kar liya to unhon-ne apne khayalat ki khabar di. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke bila shubah wo haq par hain aur Allah ke sachey rasool hain. achchha subah ko tum mere peechhey peechhey mere sath chalnaa. agar main (raastey mein) koi aisi baat dekhoonga jis se mujhey tumharey barey mein khatrah ho to main khada ho jaaunga. ( kisi diwar ke qareeb ( maano mujhey peshab karna hai, us waqt tum mera intizar na karna aur jab main phir chalney lagoon to mere peechhey aa jana taake koi samajh na sakey ke ye donon sath hain aur is tarah jis ghar mein, main dakhil hon tum bhi dakhil ho jaanaa. unhon-ne aisa hi kya aur peechhey peechhey chaley yahan tak ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaey. aap ki baatein suniin aur wahin Islam ley aaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke ab apni qaum ghifaar mein wapas jao aur unhein mera haal bataao yahan tak ke jab hamarey ghalbe ka ilm tum ko ho jaey (to phir hamarey paas aa jana) Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main un Quraishiyon ke majme' mein pukar kar kalima tauheed ka elaan karunga. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan se wapas wo masjide-Haraam mein aaey aur buland awaz se kaha ke ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain.'' ye suntey hi Sara majma' un par toot padaa aur unhein itna maara ke zameen par lita diya itney mein Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke uper apne aapko daal kar Quraish se kaha afsos kya tumhen malum nahi ke ye shakhs qabila ghifaar se hai aur Sham (Syria) janey waley tumharey taajiron ka rasta idhar hi se padta hai is tarah se unse unko bachaya . phir Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) doosrey din masjide-Haraam mein aaey aur apne Islam ka izhar kya. qaum phir buri tarah un par toot padi aur maarney lagi us din bhi Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) un par aundhey pad gaey."
3862,"maine Kufa ki masjid mein Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke aik waqt tha jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Islam laney se pahley mujhey us wjah se baandh rakha tha ke maine Islam kyon qabool kya lekin tum logon ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath jo kuchh kya hai uski wjah se agar Uhud pahaad bhi apni jagah se sarak jaey to usey aisa karna hi chahiye"
3863,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke Islam laney ke baad ham log hamesha izzat se rahe.
3864,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) (Islam laney ke baad Quraish se) darey huey ghar mein baithey huey they ke abu-Amr Aas-bin-Waail Sehmi andar aaya, aik dhaarii daar chadar aur reshamii kurta pahney huey tha. wo qabila banu-Saham se tha jo zamana jahiliyat mein hamarey haleef they. Aas ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha kya baat hai? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tumhari qaum banu-Saham waley kehtey hain ke agar main musalman hua to wo mujh ko mar daalengey. Aas ne kaha ''tumhein koi nuqsan nahi pahuncha saktaa'' jab Aas ne ye kalima keh diya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir main bhi apne ko aman mein samajhta hun. iske baad Aas bahar nikla to dekha ke maidan logon se bhar gaya hai. Aas ne puchha kidhar ka rukh hai? logon ne kaha ham ibne-khitaab ki khabar leney jatey hain jo be-deen ho gaya hai. Aas ne kaha usey koi nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakta, ye suntey hi log lot gaey."
3865,"jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) Islam laey to log unke ghar ke qareeb jama ho gaey aur kehney lagey ke umr be-deen ho gaya hai. main un dinon bachcha tha aur us waqt apne ghar ki chhat par chadhaa hua tha. achcha aik shakhs aaya jo resham ki Quba pahney huey tha, us shakhs ne logon se kaha theek hai umr be-deen ho gaya lekin ye majma' kaisa hai? dekho mein umr ko panah de chuka hun. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine dekha ke uski ye baat suntey hi log alag-alag ho gaey. maine puchha ye kon sahib they? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye Aas-bin-Waail hain."
3866,"jab bhi umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kisi cheez ke mutaalliq kaha ke mera khayal hai ke ye is tarah hai to wo isi tarah hui jaisa wo iske mutaalliq apna khayal zahir kartey they. aik din wo baithey huey they ke aik khoobsurat shakhs wahan se guzraa. unhon-ne kaha ya to mera guman ghalat hai ya ye shakhs apne jahiliyat ke Deen par ab bhi qaaim hai ya ye zamana jahiliyat main apni qaum ka kaahin raha hai. us shakhs ko mere paas bulao . wo shakhs bulaya gaya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne uske samney bhi yahi baat dohraaii. is par usne kaha maine to aaj ke din ka sa mamla kabhi nahi dekha jo kisi musalman ko pesh aaya ho. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha lekin main tumharey liye zaroori qarar deta hun ke tum mujhey is silsiley mein bataao. usne iqrar kya ke zamane jahiliyat mein, main apni qaum ka kaahin tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ghaib ki jo khabrein tumhari Jinnii tumharey paas laatii thi, uski sabse hairatnaak koi baat sunaao? shakhs mazkoor ne kaha ke aik din mein bazar mein tha ke Jinnii mere paas aai. maine dekha ke wo ghabraaii hui hai, phir usne kaha jinnon ke mutaalliq tumhen malum nahi. jab se unhein aasmani khabron se rok diya gaya hai wo kis darja darey huey hain, maayoos ho rahe hain aur oontniyon ke paalaan ki kamliyon se mil gaey hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum ne sach kaha, aik martaba main bhi un dinon buton ke qareeb soyaa hua tha. aik shakhs aik bachhda laya aur us ne but par usey zabah kar diya uske andar se is qadr zor ki awaz nikli ke maine aisi shadeed cheekh kabhi nahi suni thi. usne kaha : aey dushman! aik baat batlaataa hun jis se murad mil jaey aik khub achchha bolneywaala shakhs yun kehta hai 'laa ilaaha illallaah' ye suntey hi tamam log (jo wahan maujood they) chaunk padey (chal diye) maine kaha, main to nahi janey ka, dekho iske baad kya hota hai. phir yahi awaz aai arey dushman tujh ko aik baat batlaataa hun jis se murad bar aaey aik khub achchha bolneywaala shakhs yun keh raha hai ""laa ilaaha illallaah"". us waqt mein khada hua aur abhi kuchh der nahi guzri thi ke log kehney lagey ye (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) Allah ke sachey rasool hain."
3867,"unhon-ne musalmanon ko mukhaatab karke kaha aik waqt tha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) jab Islam mein dakhil nahi huey they, to mujhey aur apni behan ko isliye baandh rakha tha ke ham Islam kyon laey aur aaj tum ne jo kuchh Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bartaw kya hai agar is par Uhud pahaad bhi apni jagah se sarak jaey to usey aisa hi karna chahiye"
3868,kuffaare-Makka ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi nishani ka mutalba kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chaand ke 2 tukdey karke dikhaa diye. yahan tak ke unhon-ne Hiraa pahaad ko un donon tukdon ke beech mein dekha.
3869,"jis waqt chaand ke 2 tukdey huey to ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina ke maidan mein maujood they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke logo ! gawah rehna aur chaand ka aik tukda doosrey se alag ho kar pahaad ki taraf chala gaya tha aur abul-Zuhaa ne bayan kya, unse Masruq ne, unse Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke shaqe-qamar ka moa'jza Makka mein pesh aaya tha. Ibrahim Nakhai ke sath uski mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin Muslim ne ki hai, unse abu-Najeeh ne bayan kya, unse Mujahid ne, unse abu-Ma'mar ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
3870,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein bila shak w shuba chaand phat gaya tha.
3871,chaand phat gaya thaa.
3872,"tum apne maamun (ameerul-momineen) Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se unke bhai Waleed bin Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet ke baare mein baat kyon nahi kartey ( hua ye tha ke logon ne is par bahut aetraz kya tha jo Usman ne Waleed ke sath kya thaa). Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padhney nikley to main unke rastey mein khada ho gaya aur maine arz kya ke mujhey aap se aik zarurat hai, aapko aik khair khwaahaana mashwara dena hai. is par unhon-ne kaha ke bhaley aadmii! tum se to main Allah ki panah mangta hun. ye sun kar main wahan se wapas chala aaya. Namaz se farigh honey ke baad main Miswar-bin-Makhrama aur ibne-abd-Yaghoos ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se jo kuchh maine kaha tha aur unhon-ne uska jawab mujhey jo diya tha, sab maine bayan kar diya. un logon ne kaha tum ne apna haq ada kar diya. abhi main us majlis mein betha tha ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka aadmi mere paas ( bulaney ke liye) aaya. un logon ne mujh se kaha tumhen Allah Taala ne imtihaan mein daala hai. aakhir mein wahan se chala aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. aap ne malum kya tum abhi jis khair-khahi ka zikr kar rahe they wo kya thi? unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir maine kaha Allah gawah hai phir maine kaha Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maboos farmaya aur un par apni kitab nazil farmai, aap un logon mein se they jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dawat par labbaik kaha tha. aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par eman laey 2 hijratein kiin (eik Habsha ko aur dusri Madina ko) aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat se faiz yaab hain aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tariqon ko dekha hai. baat ye hai ke Waleed bin Aqba ke barey mein logon mein ab bahut charcha honey laga hai. isliye aap ke liye zaroori hai ke is par (sharaab peeney ki) had qaaim karein. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya mere bhatijey ya mere bhaanjey kya tum ne bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha hai? maine arz kya ke nahi. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Deen ki baatein is tarah maine hasil ki thin jo aik kunwari ladki ko bhi apne pardey mein malum ho chuki hain. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ye sun kar phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Allah ko gawah karke farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath maboos kya aur aap par apni kitab nazil ki thi aur ye bhi theek hai ke main un logon mein se tha jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki dawat par) shuruaat hi mein) labbaik kaha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo shariiat lekar aaey they main is par eman laya aur jaisa ke tum ne kaha maine 2 hijratein kin. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat se faiz yaab hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait bhi ki. Allah ki qism ! maine aap ki nafarmani nahi ki aur na kabhi khayanat ki. aakhir Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wafat de di aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa muntakhab huey. Allah ki qism ! maine unki bhi kabhi nafarmani nahi ki aur na unke kisi maamle mein koi khayanat ki. unke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa huey maine unki bhi kabhi nafarmani nahi ki aur na kabhi khayanat ki. iske baad mein khaleefa hua. kya ab mera tum logon par wahi haq nahi hai jo unka mujh par tha? Ubaidullah ne arz kya yaqinan aap ka haq hai phir unhon-ne kaha phir un baton ki kya haqiqat hai jo tum logon ki taraf se pahunch rahi hain? jahan tak tum ne Waleed bin Aqba ke barey mein zikr kya hai to ham inshaAllah us mamley mein uski giraft haq ke sath karengey. rawi ne bayan kya ke aakhir (gawaahii ke baad) Waleed bin Aqba ko chalis (40) kode lagwaaey gaey aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke kode lagaaein . Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hi ne usko kode maarey they. is hadis ko Yunus aur Zohri ke bhatijey ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya usmein Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul is tarah bayan kya, kya tum logon par mera wahi haq nahi hai jo un logon ka tum par tha."
3873,Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne aik girjey ka zikr kya jisey unhon-ne Habsha mein dekha tha. uske andar tasweerein thin. unhon-ne uska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab unmein koi nek mard hota aur uski wafat ho jati to uski qabr ko wo log masjid banatey aur phir usmein uski tasweerein rakhtey. ye log qiyamat ke din Allah Taala ki bargah mein badtareen makhlooq hongey. ''
3874,main jab Habsha se aai to bahut kam Umr thi. mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dhaarii daar chadar inayat farmai aur phir aap ne uski dhaariyon par apna hath pher kar farmaayaa (سناه ، Mina سناه‏). Humaidii ne bayan kya ke (سناه ، Mina سناه‏) habshii zaban ka lafz hai yani achchha achchha .
3875,"(ibtidaae-Islaam mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey hotey aur ham aapko salam kartey to aap Namaz hi mein jawab inayat farmatey they. lekin jab ham Najashi ke mulk Habsha se wapas (Madeena) aaey aur ham ne (namaz padhtey mein) aapko salam kya to aap ne jawab nahi diya. Namaz ke baad ham ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham pahley aapko salam kartey they, to aap Namaz hi mein jawab inayat farmaya kartey they? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke haan, Namaz mein aadmi ko doosra kaam hota hai. Sulaiman Aamash ne bayan kya ke maine Ibrahim Nakhai se puchha aisey mauqe par aap kya kartey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke main dil mein jawab de deta hun."
3876,"jab hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hijrat Madina ki itlaa mili to ham Yaman mein they. phir ham kashtii par Sawar huey lekin ittifaq se hua ne hamari kashtii ka rukh Najashi ke mulk Habsha ki taraf kar diya. hamari mulaqat wahan Jafar bin abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) se hui (jo hijrat karke wahan maujood they) ham unhein ke sath wahan thahrey rahe, phir Madina ka rukh kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us waqt mulaqat hui jab aap khaibar fateh kar chukey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne aey kashtii waalo! 2 hijratein ki hain."
3877,"jis din Najashi (Habsha ke baadshaah) ki wafat hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aaj aik nek mard is duniya se chala gaya, utho aur apne bhai as'hama ki namaaze-janaaza padh lo.''"
3878,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najashi ke janaaza ki Namaz padhi thi aur ham saf baandh kar aap ke peechhey khadey huey. main dusri ya teesri saf mein tha.
3879,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne as'hama Najashi ki namaaze-janaaza padhi aur char martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz mein takbeer kahi. Yazid-bin-Harun ke sath is hadis ko Abdus-Samad-bin-abdul-waaris ne bhi (saleem bin hayyaan) se riwayat kya hai.
3880,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Habsha ke badshah Najashi ki maut ki khabar isi din de di thi jis din unka intiqal hua tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke apne bhai ki maghfirat ke liye dua karo.
3881,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (namaaze-janaaza ke liye) eidgaah mein sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko saf basta khada kya aur uski namaaze-janaaza padhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char martaba takbeer kahi thi.
3882,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Hunain ka irada kya to farmaya ''insha'allah kal hamara qiyam khaif-banii-kinaana mein hoga.'' jahan mushrekeen ne kaafir hi rehney ke liye ahad w paiman kya tha.
3883,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha aap apne chacha ( abu-Taalib (ke kya kaam aaey ke wo aap ki himaayat kya kartey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ghussa hotey they? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(isii wjah se) wo sirf takhnon tak jahannam mein hain agar main unki sifarish na karta to wo dozakh ki teh mein bilkul nichey hotey.''
3884,"jab abu-Taalib ki wafat ka waqt qareeb hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif ley gaey. us waqt wahan abu-Jahal bhi betha hua tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' chacha ! kalima ""laa ilaaha-illallaah"" aik martaba keh do, Allah ki bargah mein (aap ki bakhshish ke liye) aik yahi daleel mere hath aa jaeygi. '' is par abu-Jahal aur Abdullaah-bin-abii-Umayya ne kaha : aey abu-Taalib ! kya abdul-Muttalib ke Deen se tum phir jaaogey! ye donon unhi par zor detey rahe aur aakhiri kalima jo unki zaban se nikla , wo ye tha ke main abdul-Muttalib ke Deen par qaaim hun. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main unke liye us waqt tak maghfirat talab karta rahunga jab tak mujhey is se mana na kar diya jaeyga chunanche ( sura baraah mein) ye aayat nazil huii ما كان للنبي والذين آمنوا أن يستغفروا للمشركين ولو كانوا أولي قربى من بعد ما تبين لهم أنهم أصحاب الجحيم‏''nabii ke liye aur musalmanon ke liye munasib nahi hai ke mushrekeen ke liye dua'ae-maghfirat karein chahe wo unke naatey waley hi kyon na hon jabke unke samney ye baat waazeh ho gaee ke wo dozakhi hain.'' aur sura Qasas mein ye aayat nazil huii إنك لا تهدي من أحببت‏''beshak jisey aap chaahein hidayat nahi kar saktey.''"
3885,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein aap ke chacha ka zikr ho raha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''shaayad qiyamat ke din unhein meri shafaat kaam aa jaey aur unhein sirf takhnon tak jahannam mein rakha jaey jis se unka dimagh khaulega. ''ham se Ibrahim bin Hamza ne bayan kya, kaha ham se ibne- abu-Hazim aur darawardi ne bayan kya Yazeed se isi mazkura (uper zikr) hadis ki tarah, albatta is riwayat mein ye bhi hai ke abu-Taalib ke dimagh ka bheja us se khaulega."
3886,jab Quraish ne (mea'raaj ke waaqie ke silsiley mein) mujh ko jhutlaayaa to main Hateem mein khada ho gaya aur Allah Taala ne mere liye baitul-maqdis ko roshan kar diya aur maine usey dekh kar Quraish se iske pattey aur nishan bayan karna shuru kar diye.
3887,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse shabe-mea'raaj ka waqia bayan kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Hateem mein leta hua tha. kuchh baar Qatada ne Hateem ke bajaey hijr bayan kya ke mere paas aik sahib (Jibraaiil (Alaihissalam) ( aaey aur mera Sina chaak kya. Qatada ne bayan kya ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke yahan se yahan tak. maine Jaarood se suna jo mere qareeb hi baithey they. puchha ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki is lafz se kya murad thi? to unhon-ne kaha ke halaq se naaf tak chaak kya ( Qatada ne bayan kya ke) maine Anas se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke seeney ke uper se naaf tak chaak kya, phir mera dil nikala aur aik soney ka tasht laya gaya jo eman se bharaa hua tha, us se mera dil dhoya gaya aur pahley ki tarah rakh diya gaya. iske baad aik janwar laya gaya jo ghodey se chhota aur gadhey se bada tha aur safaid ! Jaarood ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : abu-Hamza ! kya wo burraaq tha? aap ne farmaya ke haan. uska har qadam uske muntahaaey-nazar par padta tha (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) mujhey is par Sawar kya gaya aur Jibraeel mujhey lekar chaley aasmaane-duniyaa par pahunchey to darwaza khulwaayaa, puchha gaya kon sahib hain? unhon-ne bataya ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) puchha gaya aur aap ke sath kon hai? aap ne bataya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . puchha gaya, kya unhein bulaney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha? unhon-ne jawab diya ke haan. is par awaz aai (unhein ( khush aamadeed ! kya hi Mubarak aaney waley hain wo , aur darwaza khol diya. jab main andar gaya to maine wahan Adam (Alaihissalam) ko dekha, Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ye aap ke baabaa Adam (Alaihissalam) hain unhein salam keejiye. maine unko salam kya aur unhon-ne jawab diya aur farmaya : khush aamadeed nek betey aur nek Nabi ! Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) uper chadhey aur doosrey aasman par aaey wahan bhi darwaza khulwaya awaz aai kon sahib aaey hain? bataya ke Jibraeel (al). puchha gaya aap ke sath aur koi sahib bhi hain? kaha Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . puchha gaya kya aapko unhein bulaney ke liye bheja gaya tha? unhon-ne jawab diya ke haan. phir awaz aai unhein khush aamadeed . kya hi achchhey aaney waley hain wo . phir darwaza khula aur main andar gaya to wahan Yahya aur Esa (Alaihissalam) maujood they. ye donon khala zaad bhai hain. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ye Esa aur Yahya (Alaihissalam) hain inhein salam keejiye. maine salam kya aur un hazraat ne mere salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya khush aamadeed nek Nabi aur nek bhai! yahan se Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) mujhey teesrey aasman ki taraf lekar chadhey aur darwaza khulwaayaa. puchha gaya kon sahib aaey hain? jawab diya ke Jibraaiil. puchha gaya aur aap ke sath kon sahib aaey hain? jawab diya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . puchha gaya kya unhein laney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha? jawab diya ke haan. is par awaz aai unhein khush aamadeed . kya hi achchhey aaney waley hain wo , darwaza khula aur jab main andar dakhil hua to wahan Yusuf (Alaihissalam) maujood they. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ye Yusuf hain inhein salam kijiye maine salam kya to unhon-ne jawab diya aur farmaya : khush aamadeed nek Nabi aur nek bhai ! phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) mujhey lekar uper chadhey aur chauthey aasman par pahunchey darwaza khulwaya to puchha gaya kon sahib hain? bataya ke Jibraeel ! puchha gaya aur aap ke sath kon hai? kaha ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . puchha gaya kya unhein bulaney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha? jawab diya ke haan! kaha ke unhein khush aamadeed. kya hi achchhey aaney waley hain wo ! ab darwaza khula jab main wahan Idrees (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ye Idrees (Alaihissalam) hain inhein salam kijiye maine unhein salam kya aur unhon-ne jawab diya aur farmaya khush aamadeed paak bhai aur nek Nabi . phir mujhey lekar paanchwein aasman par aaey aur darwaza khulwaya puchha gaya kon sahib hain? jawab diya ke Jibraaiil. puchha gaya aap ke sath kon sahib aaey hain? jawab diya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . puchha gaya ke unhein bulaney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha? jawab diya ke haan. ab awaz aai khush aamadeed kya hi achchhey aaney waley hain wo. yahan jab main Harun (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne bataya ke ye Harun hain inhein salam kijiye maine unhein salam kya unhon-ne jawab ke baad farmaya khush aamadeed nek Nabi aur nek bhai ! yahan se lekar mujhey aagey badhey aur chhatey aasman par pahunchey aur darwaza khulwaya puchha gaya kon sahib aaey hain? bataya ke Jibraeel, puchha gaya aap ke sath koi doosrey sahib bhi aaey hain? jawab diya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . puchha gaya kya unhein bulaney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha? jawab diya ke haan. phir kaha unhein khush aamadeed, kya hi achchhey aaney waley hain wo. main jab wahan Musa (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke ye Musa (Alaihissalam) hain inhein salam kijiye , maine salam kya aur unhon-ne jawab ke baad farmaya khush aamadeed nek Nabi aur nek bhai ! jab main aagey badha to wo roney lagey kisi ne puchha aap ro kyon rahe hain? to unhon-ne farmaya main is par ro raha hun ke ye ladka mere baad Nabi bana kar bheja gaya lekin jannat mein uski ummat ke log meri ummat se zyada hongey. phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) mujhey lekar saatwen aasman ki taraf gaey aur darwaza khulwaya . puchha gaya kon sahib aaey hain? jawab diya ke Jibraeel, puchha gaya aur aap ke sath kon sahib aaey hain? jawab diya ke Muhammad (sl). puchha gaya kya unhein bulaney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha? jawab diya ke haan. kaha ke unhein khush aamadeed. kya hi achchhey aaney waley hain wo, main jab andar gaya to Ibrahim tashrif rakhtey they. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke ye aap ke baabaa hain, inhein salam kijiye . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine unko salam kya to unhon-ne jawab diya aur farmaya khush aamadeed nek Nabi aur nek betey! phir Sidratul-Muntahaa ko mere samney kar diya gaya maine dekha ke iske phal maqaame-hijr ke matkon ki tarah (badey badey) they aur uske pattey haathiyon ke kaan ki tarah they. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke ye Sidaratul-muntahaa hai. wahan maine char nehrein dekhiin, 2 baatinii (androonii) aur 2 zaahirii. maine puchha aey Jibraaiil! ye kya hain? unhon-ne bataya ke jo 2 baatinii nehrein hain wo jannat se talluq rakhti hain aur 2 zahiri nahrein, neel aur Furaat hain. phir mere samney baitul-Ma'moor ko laya gaya, wahan mere samney aik glaas mein sharab aik mein doodh aur aik mein shehad laya gaya. maine doodh ka glaas ley liya to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya yahi fitrat hai aur aap is par qaaim hain aur aap ki ummat bhi! phir mujh par rozaana pachaas namazein farz ki gaiin. main wapas hua aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra to unhon-ne puchha kis cheez ka aapko hukm hua? maine kaha ke rozaana pachaas waqt ki namazon kaa. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya lekin aap ki ummat mein itni taqat nahi hai. is se pahley mera waasta logon se pad chuka hai aur Bani-Israeel ka mujhey talkh tajriba hai. isliye aap apne rab ke huzoor mein dobara jaaiye aur apni ummat par kami ke liye arz kijiye . chunanche main Allah Taala ke darbar mein dobara hazir hua aur kami ke liye kaha to das waqt ki namazein kam kar di gain . phir main jab waapsii mein Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra to unhon-ne phir wahi sawal kya main dobara baargaahe-rab taala mein hazir hua aur us martaba bhi das waqt ki namazein kam huin. phir main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra aur to unhon-ne wahi mutalba kya maine is martaba bhi baargaahe-rab taala mein hazir ho kar das waqt ki namazein kam karaaein. Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se phir guzra unhon-ne apni raey ka izhar kya phir baargaahe-Ilaahii mein hazir hua to mujhey das waqt ki namazon ka hukm hawa mein wapas honey laga to aap ne phir wahi kaha ab baargaahe-Ilaahii mein hazir hua to rozaana sirf panch waqt ki namazon ka hukm baqi raha. Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to aap ne malum farmaya ab kya hukm hua? maine Musa (Alaihissalam) ko bataya ke rozaana panch waqt ki namazon ka hukm hua hai. farmaya ke aap ki ummat iski bhi taqat nahi rakhti mera waasta aap se pahley logon se pad chuka hai aur Bani-Israeel ka mujhey talkh tajriba hai. apne rab ke darbar mein phir hazir ho kar kami ke liye arz keejiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya rab taala se main bahut sawal kar chuka aur ab mujhey sharm aati hai. ab main bas isi par razi hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir jab main wahan se guzarney laga to nidaa aai '' maine apna fareeza jari kar diya aur apne bandon par kami kar chukaa.''"
3888,Allah ke irshad ( وما جعلنا الرؤيا التي أريناك إلا فتنة للناس‏ (aur jo khuwab ham ne aapko dikhaya us se maqsad sirf logon ka imtihaan tha) farmaya ke usmein rua'yaa se aankh se dekhnaa hi murad hai. jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us meraaj ki raat mein dikhaya gaya tha jis mein aapko baitul-maqdis tak ley jaya gaya tha aur Quran Majeed main ( الشجرة الملعونة (ka zikr aaya hai wo thoohad ka darakht hai.
3889,"maine Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke wo jange-Tabook mein Sharik na honey ka lamba waqia bayan kartey they ibne-Bukair ne apni riwayat mein bayan kya ke Kab ne kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Aqba ki raat mein hazir tha jab ham ne Islam par qaaim rehney ka pukhta ahad kya tha, mere nazdeek ( Lailatal-Aqbaa ki bait ( badr ki ladai mein haziri se bhi zyada pasandida hai bhale hi logon mein badr ka charcha us se zyada hai."
3890,mere 2 maamun mujhey bhi bait Aqba mein sath le gaey they. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari ne kaha ke ibne-Uena ne bayan kya unmein se aik Baraa-bin-Ma'roor (Raziallahu anhu) they.
3891,"Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main mere walid aur mere 2 maamun teenon bait Aqba karne walon mein Sharik they."
3892,"hamein abu-Idrees Aaizullaah-bin-abdullaah ne khabar di ke Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) un sahaba mein se they jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath badr ki ladai mein shirkat ki thi aur Aqba ki raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ahad kya tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us waqt aap ke paas sahaba ki aik jamat thi, ke aao mujh se is baat ka ahad karo ke Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraaogey, chori na karogey, zina na karogey, apni aulad ko qatl na karogey, apni taraf se ghad kar kisi par tohmat na lagaaogey aur achi baton mein meri nafarmani na karogey, to jo shakhs apne us ahad par qaaim rahega iska ajr Allah ke zimma hai aur jis shakhs ne usmein kami ki aur Allah Taala ne usey chipa rehney diya to uska mamla Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hai, chahey to is par saza de aur chahey maaf kar de. Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya chunanche maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un baton par bait ki."
3893,"main un naqeebon mein se tha jinhoney ( Aqba ki raat mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi. aap ne bayan kya ke ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska ahad kya tha ke ham Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraayengey, chori nahi karengey, zina nahi karengey, kisi aisey shakhs ko qatl nahi karengey jiska qatl Allah Taala ne haram qarar diya hai, loot mar nahi karengey aur na Allah ki nafarmani karengey, jannat ke badley main, agar ham apne waadey mein poorey utrey. lekin agar ham ne usmein kuchh khilaf kya to uska faisla Allah par hai."
3894,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mera nikah jab hua to meri umr chh saal ki thi, phir ham Madina ( hijrat karke ( aaey aur bani Haris bin khazraj ke yahan qiyam kya. yahan aa kar mujhey bukhar chadhaa aur uski wjah se mere baal girney lagey. phir moondhon tak khub baal ho gaey phir aik din meri walida umme-Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) aaiin. us waqt main apni chand saheliyon ke sath jhoolaa jhol rahi thi unhon-ne mujhey pukara to main hazir ho gaee. mujhey kuchh malum nahi tha ke mere sath unka kya irada hai. aakhir unhon-ne mera hath pakad kar ghar ke darwaza ke paas khada kar diya aur mera saans phoolaa ja raha tha. thodi der mein jab mujhey kuchh sukoon hua to unhon-ne thoda sa pani lekar mere munh aur sar par pheraa. phir ghar ke andar mujhey le gaiin. wahan Ansar ki chand auratein maujood thin, jinhonney mujhey dekh kar dua di ke khair w barkat aur achchha naseeb lekar aai ho. meri maan ne mujhey unhiin ke hawale kar diya aur unhon-ne mujhey sajaayaa. iske baad din chadhey achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur unhon-ne mujhey aap ke sipurd kar diya meri umr us waqt nau (9) saal thi."
3895,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mujhey 2 martaba khuwab mein dikhai gaee ho. maine dekha ke tum aik reshamii kapdey mein liptii hui ho aur kaha ja raha hai ke ye aap ki biwi hain unka chehra kholiye. maine chehra khol kar dekha to tum thin. maine sochaa ke agar ye khuwab Allah Taala ki taraf se hai to wo khud usko pura farmaaeyga.''
3896,Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ki wafat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Madina ko hijrat se teen saal pahley ho gaee thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aap ki wafat ke taqriban 2 saal baad Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya us waqt unki umr chh saal thi jab rukhsati hui to wo nau (9) saal ki thin.
3897,"ham Khubaab-bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye gaey to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham ne sirf Allah ki khushnoodii hasil karne ke liye hijrat ki thi. Allah Taala hamein iska ajr dega. phir hamarey bahut se sathi is duniya se uth gaey aur unhon-ne (duniyaa mein) apne aamaal ka phal nahi dekha. unhiin mein Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid kiye gaey they aur sirf aik dhaarii daar chadar chhodi thi. ( kafan detey waqt) jab ham unki chadar se unka sar dhaanktey to paon khul jatey aur paon dhaanktey to sar khul jata. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke unka sar dhaank dein aur paon par izkhir ghaas daal dein. (taake chhup jayen (aur ham mein aisey bhi hain ke (is duniya mein bhi) unke aamaal ka mewa paak gaya, to wo usko chun rahe hain."
3898,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke aamaal niyat par moquf hain. to jiska maqsad , hijrat se duniya kamaanaa ho wo apne usi maqsad ko hasil kar sakega. agar maqsad hijrat se kisi aurat se shadi karna ho to wo bhi apne maqsad tak pahunch sakega. lekin jinka hijrat se maqsad, Allah aur uske rasool ki raza-mandi hogi to usi ki hijrat Allah aur uske rasool ke liye samjhii jaeygi."
3899,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke fateh Makka ke baad (Makka se Madina ki taraf ( hijrat baqi nahi rahi.
3900,"Ubaid-bin-Umair Lesi ke sath main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur ham ne unse fateh Makka ke baad hijrat ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne kaha ke aik waqt tha jab musalman apne Deen ki hifazat ke liye Allah Taala aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf ahad karke aata tha. us khatrah ki wjah se ke kahin wo fitna mein na pad jaey lekin ab Allah Taala ne Islam ko ghalib kar diya hai aur aaj ( sar zameene-arab mein) insan jahan bhi chahey apne rab ki ibadat kar sakta hai, albatta jihad aur niyat sawab baqi hai."
3901,"aey Allah ! to janta hai ke us se zyada mujhey aur koi cheez pasandida nahi ke terey rastey mein, main us qaum se jihad karun jisne terey rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jhutlaayaa aur unhein (unke watan Makka se) nikala . aey Allah ! lekin aisa malum hota hai ke tu ney hamarey aur unke darmyan ladai ka silsila khatm kar diya hai. aur Abaan-bin-Yazeed ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne bayan kya, unse unke walid ne aur unhein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke (ye alfaz Sad (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they) (من قوم كذبوا نبيك وأخرجوه من قريش‏) yaanii jinhoney terey rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jhutlaayaa, bahar nikal diya. us se Quraish ke kaafir murad hain."
3902,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chalis (40) saal ki umr mein rasool banaya gaya tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Makka Mukarrama mein 13 saal tak wahi aati rahi iske baad aapko hijrat ka hukm hua aur aap ne hijrat ki haalat mein das saal guzaarey. (Madina mein) jab aap ki wafat hui to aap ki umr tiresath saal ki thi.
3903,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nabwooat ke baad Makka mein 13 saal qiyam kya aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap ki umr tiresath saal ki thi.
3904,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par baithey, farmaya ''apne aik nek bandey ko Allah Taala ne ikhtiyar diya ke duniya ki ne'maton mein se jo wo chahey usey apne liye pasand kar ley ya jo Allah Taala ke yahan hai) aakhirat mein) usey pasand kar ley. us bandey ne Allah Taala ke yahan milney wali cheez ko pasand kar liya. ''is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey aur arz kya hamarey maan-baap aap par fidaa hun. (abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain) hamein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke us roney par hairat hui, kuchh logon ne kaha us buzurg ko dekhiye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to aik bandey ke mutaalliq khabar de rahe hain jisey Allah Taala ne duniya ki ne'maton aur jo Allah ke paas hai is mein se kisi ke pasand karne ka ikhtiyar diya tha aur ye keh rahe hain ke hamarey maan-baap aap par fidaa hon. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ko un 2 chizon mein se aik ka ikhtiyar diya gaya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ham mein sabse zyada is baat ko jantey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke logon mein sabse zyada apni sohbat aur maal ke zariey mujh par ehsan karne waley Abu-Bakar hain. agar main apni ummat mein se kisi ko apna khaleel bana sakta to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaataa, albatta Islami rishta unke sath kafi hai. masjid mein koi darwaza ab khula hua baqi na rakha jaey siwaey Abu-Bakar ke ghar ki taraf khulney waley darwazey ke."
3905,"jab se maine hosh sanbhaalaa maine apne maan-baap ko deene-Islam hi par paya aur koi din aisa nahi guzarta tha jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey ghar subah w Sham donon waqt tashrif na latey hun. phir jab (Makka mein) musalmanon ko sataayaa janey laga to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Habsha ki hijrat ka irada karke nikley. jab aap maqam barak ghamaad par pahunchey to aap ki mulaqat ibne-Daghina se hui jo qabila qaara ka sardaar tha. us ne puchha abu-Bakar! kahan ka irada hai? unhon-ne kaha ke meri qaum ne mujhey nikal diya hai ab maine irada kar liya hai ke mulk mulk ki sair karun (aur aazadi ke saath) apne rab ki ibadat karun. ibne-Daghina ne kaha lekin abu-Bakar! tum jaisey insan ko apne watan se na khud nikalnaa chahiye aur na usey nikala jana chahiye tum mohtajon ki madad kartey ho, sila rehmii kartey ho, be kason ka bojh uthatey ho, mehman nawazi kartey ho aur haq par qaaim rehney ki wjah se kisi par aaney wali museebaton mein uski madad kartey ho, main tumhen panah deta hun wapas chalo aur apne Shahar hi main apne rab ki ibadat karo. chunanche wo wapas aagey aur ibne-Daghina bhi aap ke sath wapas aaya. iske baad ibne-Daghinaa Quraish ke tamam sardaaron ke yahan Sham ke waqt gaya aur sabse usne kaha ke Abu-Bakar jaisey shakhs ko na khud nikalnaa chahiye aur na nikala jana chahiye kya tum aisey shakhs ko nikal doge jo mohtajon ki imdaad karta hai, sila rehmii karta hai, be-kason ka bojh uthata hai, mehman nawazi karta hai aur haq ki wjah se kisi par aaney wali museebaton mein uski madad karta hai? Quraish ne ibne-Daghina ki panah se inkar nahi kya sirf itna kaha ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se keh do ke apne rab ki ibadat apne ghar ke andar hi kya karein, wahin Namaz padhein aur jo ji chahey wahin padhein, apni ibaadaat se hamein takleef na pahunchaaein, iska izhar na karein kyonke hamein iska dar hai ke kahin hamari auratein aur bachchey us fitna mein na mubtala ho jaaein. ye baatein ibne-Daghina ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi aa kar keh dein kuchh dinon tak to aap is par qaaim rahe aur apne ghar ke andar hi apne rab ki ibadat kartey rahe, na Namaz sare-aam padhtey aur na ghar ke siwa kisi aur jagah tilawat Quran kartey they, lekin phir unhon-ne kuchh sochaa aur apne ghar ke samney Namaz padhney ke liye aik jagah banai jahan aap ne Namaz padhni shuru ki aur tilaawate-Qur'aan bhi wahin karne lagey. nateeja ye hua ke wahan mushrekeen ki aurton aur bachchon ka majma' honey laga. wo sab hairat aur pasandeedgii ke sath dekhtey raha kartey they. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) badey narm dil insan they. jab Quran Majeed ki tilawat kartey to aansuon ko rok na saktey they. us soorate-haal se mushrekeene-Quraish ke sardaar ghabraa gaey aur unhon-ne ibne-Daghina ko bula bheja jab ibne-Daghina unke paas aaya to unhon-ne us se kaha ke ham ne Abu-Bakar ke liye tumhari panah is shart ke sath taslim ki thi ke apne rab ki ibadat wo apne ghar ke andar kya karein lekin unhon-ne shart ki khilaf warzi ki hai aur apne ghar ke samney Namaz padhney ke liye aik jagah bana kar sare-aam Namaz padhney aur tilaawate-qur'aan karne lagey hain. hamein iska dar hai ke kahin hamari auratein aur bachchey us fitney mein na mubtala ho jayen isliye tum unhein rok do, agar unhein ye shart manzoor ho ke apne rab ki ibadat sirf apne ghar ke andar hi kya karein to wo aisa kar saktey hain lekin agar wo izhar hi karein to unse kaho ke tumhari panah wapas de dein, kyonke hamein ye pasand nahi ke tumhari di hui panah mein ham dakhal andazi karein lekin Abu-Bakar ke us izhar ko bhi ham bardasht nahi kar saktey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir ibne-Daghina abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaya aur us ne kaha ke jis shart ke sath maine aap ke sath ahad kya tha wo aapko malum hai, ab ya aap us shart par qaaim rahiye ya phir mere ahad ko wapas kijiye kyonke ye mujhey gawara nahi ke Arab ke kanon tak ye baat pahunchey ke maine aik shakhs ko panah di thi. lekin usmein ( Quraish ki taraf se) dakhal andazi ki gaee. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main tumhari panah wapas karta hun aur apne rab azz-w-jall ki panah par razi aur khush hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un dinon Makka mein tashrif rakhtey they. aap ne musalmanon se farmaya ke tumhari hijrat ki jagah mujhey khuwab mein dikhai gaee hai wahan khajoor ke baghaat hain aur 2 pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan waaqe hai, chunanche jinhein hijrat karni thi unhon-ne Madina ki taraf hijrat ki aur jo log sar-zameene-Habsha hijrat karke chaley gaey they wo bhi Madina chaley aaey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Madina hijrat ki taiyaarii shuru kar di lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke kuchh dinon ke liye intizar karo. mujhey tawaqqoa' hai ke hijrat ki ijazat mujhey bhi mil jaeygi Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : kya waqei aapko bhi uski tawaqqoa' hai, mere bap aap par fidaa hon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rifaaqat safar ke khayal se apna irada multawii kar diya aur 2 oontniyon ko jo unke paas thin keekar ke patey khilaa kar taiyaar karne lagey char mahiney tak. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya, unse Urwa ne ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, aik din ham Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar baithey huey they bhari do-pahar thi ke kisi ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar par rumaal daley tashrif la rahe hain, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka mamool (routine) hamarey yahan us waqt aaney ka nahi tha Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par mere maan-baap fidaa hun. aisey waqt mein aap kisi khas wjah se hi tashrif la rahe hongey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur andar aaney ki ijazat chahi Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko ijazat di to aap andar dakhil huey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya us waqt yahan se thodi der ke liye sab ko utha 2 Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya yahan is waqt to sab ghar ke hi aadmi hain, mere bap aap par fidaa hon, ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad farmaya ke mujhey hijrat ki ijazat de di gaee hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon, ya Rasulullah ! kya mujhey safar mein sath rehney ka sharf hasil ho sakega ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan. unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon un donon mein se aik ontni aap ley liijiye! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin qeemat se, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir ham ne jaldi jaldii unke liye taiyaariyaan shuru kar dein aur kuchh khane-pine ka saman aik thailey mein rakh diya. Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne patkey ke tukdey karke thailey ka munh us se baandh diya aur usi wjah se unka naam zaatunaqaatain (2 patkey wali) pad gaya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Jabale-Saur ke ghaar mein padao kya aur teen raatein guzaariin. Abdullaah-bin-abii-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) raat wahin ja kar guzara kartey they, ye naujawaan bahut samajhdaar they aur zaheen behad they. sahar ke waqt wahan se nikal aatey aur subah sawerey hi Makka pahunch jatey jaisey wahin raat guzri ho. phir jo kuchh yahan suntey aur jiske zariey un hazraat ke khilaf kaarrwaaii ke liye koi tadbeer ki jati to usey mehfooz rakhtey aur jab andhera chhaa jata to tamam ittilaaat yahan aa kar pahunchaatey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghulam Aamir-bin-Fuhaira (Raziallahu anhu) aap har 2 ke liye qareeb hi doodh dene wali bakri charaayaa kartey they aur jab kuchh raat guzar jati to usey ghaar mein latey they. aap usi par raat guzaarey us doodh ko garm lohey ke zariey garm kar liya jata tha. subah munh andherey hi Aamir-bin-Fuhaira (Raziallahu anhu) ghaar se nikal aatey they un teen raaton mein rozaana unka yahi dastoor tha Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne banii-Dail jo bani abd-bin-Adii ki shaakh thi, ke aik shakhs ko rasta bataaney ke liye ujrat par apne sath rakha tha. ye shakhs raston ka bada maahir tha. aale-Aas-bin-Waail Sehmi ka ye haleef bhi tha aur kuffaare-Quraish ke Deen par qaaim tha. un buzurgon ne is par aitimad kya aur apne donon oont iske hawale kar diye. qarar ye paya tha ke teen raatein guzaar kar ye shakhs ghaare-saur mein unse mulaqat kare. chunanche teesri raat ki subah ko wo donon oont lekar ( aa gaya) ab Aamir-bin-Fuhaira (Raziallahu anhu) aur ye rasta bataaney wala un hazraat ko sath lekar rawaana huey saahil ke rastey se hotey huey."
3906,"hamarey paas kuffaare-Quraish ke qaasid aaey aur ye pesh kash! ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko agar koi shakhs qatl kar de ya qaid kar laey to usey har aik ke badley mein aik so oont diye jaengey. main apni qaum bani mudlij ki aik majlis mein betha hua tha ke unka aik aadmi samney aaya aur hamarey qareeb khada ho gaya. ham abhi baithey huey they. usne kaha suraaqa! saahil par main abhi chand saaey dekh kar aa raha hun mera khayal hai ke wo Muhammad aur unke sathi hi hain (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . Suraqa ne kaha, main samajh gaya iska khayal sahi hai lekin maine us se kaha ke wo log nahi hain maine falan-falan aadmi ko dekha hai hamarey samney se usi taraf gaey hain. iske baad main majlis mein thodi der aur betha raha aur phir uthtey hi ghar gaya aur londi se kaha ke mere ghodey ko lekar teeley ke peechhey chali jaey aur wahin mera intizar karey, iske baad maine apna neza uthaya aur ghar ki pusht ki taraf se bahar nikal aaya. main neze ki nauk se zameen par lakeer kheenchtaa hua chala gaya aur uper ke hissey ko chhipaaey huey tha. ( Suraqa ye sab kuchh isliye kar raha tha ke kisi ko khabar na ho warna wo bhi mere inaam mein Sharik ho jaaeyga) mein ghodey ke paas aa kar is par Sawar hua aur sabaa raftaarii ke sath usey ley chalaa, jitni jaldi ke sath bhi mere liye mumkin tha, aakhir maine unko pa hi liya. usi waqt ghodey ne thokar khaaii aur mujhey zameen par gira diya. lekin main khada ho gaya aur apna hath tarkash ki taraf badhaya usmein se teer nikal kar maine faal nikaalii ke aaya mein unhein nuqsan pahuncha sakta hun ya nahi. faal ( ab bhi) wo nikli jisey main pasand nahi karta tha. lekin main dobara apne ghodey par Sawar ho gaya aur teeron ke faal ki parwah nahi ki. phir mera ghoda mujhey tezi ke sath daudaaey liye ja raha tha. aakhir jab maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qirat suni , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri taraf koi tawajjoh nahi kar rahe they lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) baar-baar mud kar dekhtey they, to mere ghodey ke aagey ke donon paon zameen mein dhans gaey jab wo takhnon tak dhans gaya to main uske uper gir padaa aur usey uthney ke liye daantaa maine usey uthaney ki koshish ki lekin wo apne paon zameen se nahi nikal saka. badi mushkil se jab us ne poori tarah khadey honey ki koshish ki to uske aagey ke paon se muntashir sa ghubaar uth kar dhoein ki tarah aasman ki taraf chadhney laga. maine teeron se faal nikaalii lekin is martaba bhi wahi faal aai jisey main pasand nahi karta tha. us waqt maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aman ke liye pukaaraa. meri awaz par wo log khadey ho gaey aur main apne ghodey par Sawar ho kar unke paas aaya. un tak burey iraadey ke sath pahunchne se jis tarah mujhey rok diya gaya tha. usi se mujhey yaqin ho gaya tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dawat ghalib aa kar rahegii. isliye maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke aap ki qaum ne aap ke maarney ke liye so oonton ke inaam ka elaan kya hai. phir maine aapko Quraish ke iradon ki itlaa di. maine un hazraat ki khidmat mein kuchh khane-pine ka saman pesh kya lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey qabool nahi farmaya mujh se kisi aur cheez ka bhi mutalba nahi kya sirf itna kaha ke hamarey mutaalliq raazdaarii se kaam lena lekin maine arz kya ke aap mere liye aik amn ki tahreer likh dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aamir-bin-Fuhaira (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya aur unhon-ne chamdey ke aik tukdey par amn ki tahreer likh di. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badhey. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya aur unhein Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mulaqat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se hui jo musalmanon ke aik tijarati qaafile ke sath Sham (Syria) se wapas aa rahe they. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein safaid poshak pesh ki. idhar Madina mein bhi musalmanon ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Makka se hijrat ki itlaa ho chuki thi aur ye log rozaana subah ko maqaame-Harra tak aatey aur intizar kartey rahtey lekin do-pahar ki garmi ki wjah se (do-pahar ko) unhein wapas jana padta tha. aik din jab bahut lambey intizar ke baad sab log aagey aur apne ghar pahunch gaey to aik Yahudi apne aik mahal par kuchh dekhney chadhaa. usne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sathiyon ko dekha safaid safaid chaley aa rahe hain. (ya tezi se jaldi-jaldi aa rahe hain) jitna aap nazdeek ho rahe they itni hi door se pani ki tarah retii ka chamaknaa kam hota jata. Yahudi be ikhtiyar chilla utha ke aey Arab ke logo ! tumharey ye buzurg sardaar aagey jinka tumhen intizar tha. musalman hathiyar lekar daud padey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka maqam Harra par istiqbaal kya. aap ne unke sath dahini taraf ka rasta ikhtiyar kya aur bani Amr-bin-Auf ke mohalle mein qiyam kya. ye rabeeul-awwal ka mahina aur peer ka din tha Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon se milney ke liye khadey ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh baithey rahe. Ansar ke jin logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us se pahley nahi dekha tha, wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hi ko salam kar rahe they. lekin jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par dhoop padney lagi to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni chadar se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par saaya kya. us waqt sab logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pehchan liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Amr-bin-Auf mein taqriban das raaton tak qiyam kya aur wo masjid ( Quba ( jiski buniyad taqwa par qaaim hai wo usi doran mein tameer hui aur aap ne usmein Namaz padhi, phir (Jum'a ke din) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ontni par Sawar huey aur sahaba bhi aap ke sath paidal rawaana huey. aakhir aap ki sawari Madina Munawra mein us maqam par aa kar baith gaee jahan ab masjide-Nabawi hai. us maqam par chand musalman un dinon Namaz ada kya kartey they. ye jagah Suhel aur Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) 2 yateem bachchon ki thi aur khajoor ka yahan khaliyiaan lagta tha. ye donon bachchey Asad-bin-Zaraarah (Raziallahu anhu) ki parwarish mein they jab aap ki ontni wahan baith gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya inshaAllah yahi hamarey qiyam ki jagah hogi. iske baad aap ne donon yateem bachchon ko bulaya aur unse us jagah ka mamla karna chaha taake wahan masjid tameer ki ja sakey. donon bachchon ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! ham ye jagah aapko muft de dengey , lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muft taur par qabool karne se inkar kya. zameen ki qeemat ada karke ley li aur wahin masjid tameer ki. uski tameer ke waqt khud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath enton ke dhoney mein Sharik they. iint dhotey waqt aap farmatey jatey they ke ''ye bojh khaibar ke bojh nahi hain balke iska ajr w sawab Allah ke yahan baqi rehney wala hai is mein bahut tahaarat aur paakii hai'' aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua farmatey they ke ''aey Allah ! ajr to bas aakhirat hi ka hai, isliye to Ansar aur muhajireen par apni rehmat nazil farmaa.'' is tarah aap ne aik musalman shaair ka sher padha jinka naam mujhey malum nahi, ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke hadison se hamein ye ab tak malum nahi hua ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us sher ke siwa kisi bhi shaair ke poorey sher ko kisi mauqe par padha ho."
3907,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Madina hijrat karke janey lagey to maine aap donon ke liye naashta taiyaar kya. maine apne walid ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha ke mere patkey ke siwa aur koi cheez us waqt mere paas aisi nahi jis se main us naashte ko baandh dun. is par unhon-ne kaha ke phir iske 2 tukdey kar lo. chunanche maine aisa hi kya aur us waqt se mera naam zaatun-Naqaatain (2 patkon wali) ho gaya aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Asma ko do patkon wali kaha,"
3908,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina ke liye rawaana huey to Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham ne aap ka peechhaa kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye baddua ki to uska ghoda zameen mein dhans gaya. us ne arz kya ke mere liye Allah se dua kijiye (ke is museebat se nijat de) mein aap ka koi nuqsan nahi karunga, aap ne uske liye dua ki. (uska ghoda zameen se nikal aayaa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik martaba rastey mein piyaas malum hui itney mein aik charwaha guzra Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine aik piyala liya aur us main (rewad ki aik bakri ka ( thoda sa doodh dohaa, wo doodh maine aap ki khidmat mein la kar pesh kya jisey aap ne nosh farmaya ke mujhey khushi hasil hui."
3909,"Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) unke pet mein they, unhiin dinon jab hamal ki muddat bhi poori ho chuki thi, main Madina ke liye rawaana hui yahan pahunch kar maine Quba mein padao kya aur yahin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) paida huey. phir main unhein lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aap ki god mein usey rakh diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik khajoor talab farmai aur usey chabaa kar aap ne Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke munh mein usey rakh diya. chunanche sabse pehli cheez jo Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke pet mein dakhil hui wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka Mubarak luaab tha. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmai aur Allah se unke liye barkat talab ki. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sabse pahley bachchey hain jinki paidaaish hijrat ke baad hui. Zakariya ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Khaalid-bin-Mukhlid ne ki hai. unse Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne, unse unke walid ne aur unse Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey ko niklin thin to wo haamla thin."
3910,"sabse pahlaa bachcha jo Islam main (hijrat ke baad) paida hua, Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) hain. unhein log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik khajoor lekar usey chabaayaa phir usko unke munh mein daal diya. isliye sabse pehli cheez jo unke pet mein gaee wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka luaab Mubarak tha."
3911,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laey to Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki sawari par peechhey baithey huey they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boodhey ho gaey they aur unko log pehchantey bhi they lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi jawan malum hotey they aur aapko log aam taur se pehchantey bhi na they. bayan kya ke agar raaste mein koi milta aur poochhta ke aey abu-Bakar! ye tumharey sath kon sahib hain? to aap jawab detey ke ye mere haadii hain, mujhey rasta bataatey hain poochhney wala ye samajhta ke Madina ka rasta bataaney wala hai aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka matlab us kalam se ye tha ke aap Deen w eman ka rasta batlatey hain. aik martaba Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) peechhey mudey to aik sawar nazar aaya jo unke qareeb aa chuka tha. unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ye sawar aa gaya aur ab hamarey qareeb hi pahunchne wala hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi usey mud kar dekha aur dua farmai ke aey Allah ! usey gira de chunanche ghodii ne usey gira diya. phir jab wo hinhinaatii hui uthi to sawar ( Suraqa ( ne kaha : aey Allah ke nabii! aap jo chaahein mujhey hukm dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya apni jagah khada reh aur dekh kisi ko hamari taraf na aaney dena. rawi ne bayan kya ke wahi shakhs jo subah aap ke khilaf tha Sham jab hui to aap ka wo hathiyar tha dushman ko aap se rokney laga. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina pahunch kar) Harra ke qareeb utrey aur Ansar ko bula bhejaa. badey-badey Ansar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur donon ko salam kya aur arz kya aap Sawar ho jayen aap ki hifazat aur farmaanbardaarii ki jaeygi, chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Sawar ho gaey aur hathiyar band Ansar ne aap donon ko halqe mein ley liya. itney mein Madina mein bhi sab ko malum ho gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif la chukey hain sab log aapko dekhney ke liye bulandi par chadh gaey aur kehney lagey ke Allah ke Nabi aa gaey. Allah ke Nabi aa gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina ki taraf chaltey rahe aur (Madina pahunch kar) Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ke paas sawari se utar gaey. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) (eik Yahudi aalim ne) apne ghar walon se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr suna, wo us waqt apne aik khajoor ke baagh mein they aur khajoor jama kar rahe they unhon-ne ( suntey hi ( badi jaldi ke sath jo kuchh khajoor jama kar chukey they usey rakh dena chaha jab aap ki khidmat mein wo hazir huey to jama shuda khajoorein unke sath hi thin. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baatein sunein aur apne ghar wapas chaley aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hamarey ( nanihaalii ( rishtedaron mein kis ka ghar yahan se zyada qareeb hai? Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke meraa, aey Allah ke nabii! ye mera ghar hai aur ye iska darwaza hai farmaya ( achchha to jaao) do-pahar ko aaraam karne ki jagah hamarey liye durust karo ham do-pahar ko wahin aaraam karengey. Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya phir aap donon tashrif ley chalein , Allah Mubarak kare. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi unke ghar mein dakhil huey they ke Abdullaah-bin-Salaam bhi aagey aur kaha ke ''main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain aur ye ke aap haq ke sath Nabi banaakar bhejey gaey hain, aur Yahudi mere mutaalliq achi tarah jantey hain ke main unka sardaar hun aur unke sardaar ka betaa hun aur unmein sabse zyada jaanney wala hun aur unke sabse badey aalim ka betaa hun, isliye aap us se pahley ke mere Islam laney ka khayal unhein malum ho, bulaaiye aur unse mere barey mein malum farmaiye, kyonke unhein agar malum ho gaya ke main Islam la chuka hun to mere mutaalliq ghalat baatein kahnii shuru kar dengey. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bula bheja aur jab wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke aey yahoodiyo! afsos tum par, Allah se daro, us zaat ki qasam! jiske siwa koi maabood nahi, tum log khub jantey ho ke main Allah ka rasoole-bar-haq hun aur ye bhi ke main tumharey paas haq lekar aaya hun, phir ab Islam mein dakhil ho jao, unhon-ne kaha ke hamein malum nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is tarah teen martaba kaha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, achchha Abdullaah-bin-Salaam tum mein kon sahib hain? unhon-ne kaha hamarey sardaar aur hamarey sardaar ke betey, ham mein sabse zyada jaanney waley aur hamarey sabse badey aalim ke betey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo Islam ley aaein. phir tumhara kya khayal hoga. kehney lagey Allah unki hifazat karey, wo Islam kyon laney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ibne-Salaam! ab inke samney aa jao. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) bahar aagey aur kaha : aey yahood ! Allah se daro, us Allah ki qasam! jiske siwa koi maabood nahi tumhen khub malum hai ke aap Allah ke rasool hain aur ye ke aap haq ke sath Nabi banaey gaey hain. yahudiyon ne kaha tum jhootey ho. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse bahar chaley janey ke liye farmaayaa."
3912,"aap ne tamam muhaajireene-awwaleen ka wazeefa (apne daure-khilaafat mein) chaar-chaar hazaar chaar-chaar qiston mein muqarrar kar diya tha, lekin Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka wazeefa char qiston mein saadhey teen hazaar tha is par unse puchha gaya ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi muhajireen mein se hain. phir aap unhein char hazaar se kam kyon detey hain? to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke unhein unke waalidain hijrat karke yahan laey they. isliye wo un muhajireen ke barabar nahi ho saktey jinhoney khud hijrat ki thi."
3913,ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hijrat ki thi.
3914,ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hijrat ki to hamara maqsad sirf Allah ki raza thi aur Allah Taala hamein iska ajr bhi zaroor dega. to ham mein se kuchh to pahley hi us duniya se uth gaey aur yahan apna koi badla unhon-ne nahi paya. Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhiin mein se hain. Uhud ki ladai mein unhon-ne shahadat paai aur unke kafan ke liye hamarey paas aik kambal ke siwa aur kuchh nahi tha aur wo bhi aisa ke agar us se ham unka sar chhipaatey to unke paon khul jatey aur agar paon chhipaatey to sar khula reh jata. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke unka sar chipa diya jaey aur paon ko izkhir ghaas se chipa diya jaey. aur ham mein kuchh wo hain jinhoney apne amal ka phal us duniya mein pukhta kar liya aur ab wo usko khub chun rahe hain.
3915,"mujh se Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne poochha, kya tum ko malum hai ke mere walid umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne tumharey walid abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko kya jawab diya tha? unhon-ne kaha nahi, to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mere walid ne tumharey walid se kaha : aey abu-Musa ! kya tum is par razi ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hamara Islam , aap ke sath hamari hijrat , aap ke sath hamara jihad hamarey tamam amal jo ham ne aap ki zindagi mein kiye hain unke badle mein ham apne un aamaal se nijat pa jayen jo ham ne aap ke baad kiye hain bhale hi wo nek bhi hon bas baraabrii par mamla khatm ho jaey. is par aap ke walid ne mere walid se kaha Allah ki qasam! main is par razi nahi hun ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad bhi jihad kya, namazein padhin, rozey rakhey aur bahut se aamaal khair kiye aur hamarey hath par aik makhlooq ne Islam qabool kya, ham to iske sawab ki bhi ummeed rakhtey hain is par mere walid ne kaha ( khair abhi tum samjho ( lekin jahan tak mera sawal hai to us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai meri khahish hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein kiye huey hamarey aamaal mehfooz rahe hon aur jitney aamaal ham ne aap ke baad kiye hain un sabse iske badle mein ham nijat pa jayen aur barabar par mamla khatm ho jaey. abu-Barda kehtey hain is par maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! aap ke walid ( umr (Raziallahu anhu)) mere walid ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) se behtar they."
3916,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se maine suna ke jab unse kaha jata ke tum ne apne walid se pahley hijrat ki to wo ghussa ho jaya kartey they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaraam farma rahe they, isliye ham ghar wapas aagey phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey aap ki khidmat mein bheja aur farmaya ke ja kar dekh aao Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi bedaar huey ya nahi chunanche main aaya (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar ho chukey they) isliye andar chala gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath par bait ki phir main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bedaar honey ki khabar di. uske baad ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein daudtey huey hazir huey umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi andar gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki aur maine bhi) dobara ( bait ki."
3917,"maine Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis suni wo bayan kartey they ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se aik paalaan khareedaa aur main unke sath utha kar pahunchaney laya tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hijrat ke safar ke ka haal puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke chunkey hamari nigrani ho rahi thi (yani kuffaar hamari taak mein they) isliye ham (ghaar se) raat ke waqt bahar aaey aur poori raat aur din bhar bahut tezi ke sath chaltey rahe, jab do-pahar hui to hamein aik chattaan dikhai di. ham iske qareeb pahunchey to uski aad mein thoda sa saaya bhi maujood tha Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik chamda bichhaa diya jo mere sath tha. aap is par let gaey, aur main aas-paas ki gard jhadney laga. ittifaq se aik charwaha nazar padaa jo apni bakriyon ke thodey se rewad ke sath usi chattaan ki taraf aa raha tha uska maqsad us chattaan se wahi tha jiske liye ham yahan aaey they (yani saaya hasil karnaa) maine us se puchha ladkey to kis ka ghulam hai? us ne bataya ke falan ka hun. maine us se puchha kya tum apni bakriyon se kuchh doodh nikal saktey ho usne kaha ke haan, phir wo apne rewad se aik bakri laya to maine us se kaha ke pahley iska than jhaad lo. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir us ne kuchh doodh dohaa . mere sath pani ka aik chhaagal tha. uske munh par kapda bandhaa hua tha. ye pani maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye sath ley rakha tha. wo pani maine us doodh par itna daala ke wo nichey tak thanda ho gaya to main usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar hazir hua aur arz kya doodh nosh farmaiye ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey nosh farmaya jis se mujhey bahut khushi hasil hui. uske baad ham ne phir kooch shuru kya aur dhoondney waley log hamari talash mein they."
3918,jab main Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath unke ghar mein dakhil hua tha to aap ki sahibzadi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) leti hui thin unhein bukhar aa raha tha maine unke walid ko dekha ke unhon-ne unke rukhsar par bosa diya aur malum kya beti ! tabeeat kaisi hai?
3919,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina munawwara) tashrif laey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur koi aap ke ashaab mein aisa nahi tha jiske baal safaid ho rahe hon, isliye aap ne mahndii aur wasma ka khizaab istemal kya tha."
3920,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein sabse zyada umr Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki thi isliye unhon-ne mahndii aur wasma ka khizaab istemal kya. us se aap ke baalon ka rang khub siyaahii-maayil surkh ho gaya.
3921,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne qabila banu-kalb ki aik aurat Umme- Bakr naam ke se shadi kar li thi. phir jab unhon-ne hijrat ki to usey talaaq de aaey. us aurat se phir iske chacha zaad bhai ( Abu-Bakar Shaddad bin Aswad ( ne shadi kar li thi, ye shakhs shaair tha aur usi ne ye mashhoor Marsiya (shok geet) kuffaare-Quraish ke barey mein kaha tha ''maqaame-badr ke kunon ko main kya kahun ke unhon-ne hamein darakht sheezaa ke badey badey piyaalon se mahroom kar diya jo kabhi oont ke kohan ke gosht se behtar hua kartey they, main badr ke kunon ko kya kahoon! unhon-ne hamein gaaney wali laundiyon aur achchhey sharaabiyon se mahroom kar diya umme-bikar to mujhey salamati ki dua deti rahi lekin meri qaum ki barbadi ke baad mere liye salamati kahan hai ye rasool hamein dobara zindagi ki khabrein bayan karta hai. kahin ullu bin janey ke baad phir zindagi kis tarah mumkin hai."
3922,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ghaar mein tha. maine jo sar uthaya to qaum ke chand logon ke qadam ( bahar ( nazar aaey maine kaha, aey Allah ke Nabi ! agar unmein se kisi ne bhi nichey jhuk kar dekh liya to wo hamein zaroor dekh lega . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Abu-Bakar ! khamosh raho ham aisey 2 hain jinka tesraa Allah hai.''"
3923,"aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hijrat ka haal poochhney laga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' tujh par afsos ! hijrat to bahut mushkil hai. tumharey paas kuchh oont bhi hain? '' usne kaha ji haan hain. farmaya ''tum uski zakat ada kartey ho?'' us ne arz kya ji haan ada karta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' oontniyon ka doodh doosrey ( mohtajon ( ko bhi dohney ke liye de diya kartey ho?'' us ne arz kya ke aisa bhi karta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' unhein ghaat par ley ja kar) mohtajon ke liye) dohtey ho?'' us ne arz kya aisa bhi karta hun. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir tum saat (7) samandar paar amal karo, Allah Taala tumharey kisi amal ka bhi sawab kam nahi karega.''"
3924,sabse pahley (hijrat karke) hamarey yahan Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) aaey phir Ammar bin-Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aaey.
3925,"sabse pahley hamarey yahan Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu)) naa-beenaa ( aaey ye donon (Madina ke) musalmanon ko Quran padhna sikhatey they. iske baad Bilaal, Sad aur Ammar bin-Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) aaey. phir umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bees sahaba ko sath lekar aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Aamir-bin-Fuhaira ko sath lekar ( tashrif laey. Madina ke logon ko jitni khushi aur musarrat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tashrif aawrii se hui maine kabhi unhein kisi baat par is qadr khush nahi dekha. laundiyaan bhi (khushii mein) kehney lagiin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab tashrif laey to us se pahley main mufassal ki dusri kai Suraton ke sath ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ ( bhi seekh chuka tha."
3926,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Abu-Bakar aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bukhar chadh aaya, main unki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kya : walid saahib! aap ki tabeeat kaisi hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab bukhar chadhaa to ye sher padhney lagey. ''har shakhs apne ghar walon ke sath subah karta hai aur maut to jootii ke tasmey se bhi zyada qareeb hai. ''aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke bukhar mein jab kuchh kami hoti to zor-zor se rotey aur ye sher padhtey ''kaash mujhey ye malum ho jata ke kabhi main aik raat bhi waadiie-Makka mein guzaar sakunga jabke mere ird-gird (khushboo daar ghaas) izkhir aur Jaleel hongii, aur kya aik din bhi mujhey aisa mil sakega jab main maqam Mujanna ke pani par jaaunga aur kya shaama aur Tufail ki pahaadiyon ko aik nazar dekh sakoonga. ''Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aapko itlaa di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki اللهم حبب إلينا المدينة كحبنا مكة أو أشد ، Mina وصححها وبارك لنا في صاعها ومدها ، Mina وانقل حماها فاجعلها بالجحفة ''aey Allaah! Madina ki mohabbat hamarey dil mein itni paida kar de jitni Makka ki thi balke us se bhi zyada , yahan ki aab w hawa ko sihat bakhsh bana . hamarey liye yahan ke saa aur mudd (anaaj naapney ke paimaaney) mein barkat inayat farma aur yahan ke bukhar ko maqam Johfa mein bhej de."
3927,"main Usman ki khidmat mein hazir hua (doosri sanad) aur Bishr-ibin-Shuaib ne bayan kya ke mujh se mere walid ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne kaha, mujh se Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bayan kya aur unhein Ubaidullah bin Adii-bin khiyaar ne khabar di ke main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne hamd w shahadat padhney ke baad farmaya : ammaa ba'd! koi shak w shuba nahi ke Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath Nabi banaakar bheja, main bhi un logon mein tha jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki dawat par (shuru hi mein) labbaik kaha aur main un tamam chizon par eman laya jinhein lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maboos huey they. phir maine 2 hijrat ki aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daamaadii ka sharf mujhey hasil hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine bait ki Allah ki qasm ke maine aap ki na kabhi nafarmani ki aur na kabhi aap se dhoka bazi ki, yahan tak ke aap ka intiqal ho gaya. Shuaib ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ishaq kalbi ne bhi ki hai, unse Zohri ne us hadis ko isi tarah bayan kya."
3928,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) Mina main apne kheme ki taraf wapas aa rahe they. ye umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke aakhiri Haj ka waqia hai to unki mujh se mulaqat ho gaee. unhon-ne kaha ke (Umar (Raziallahu anhu) haajiyon ko khitab karne waley they is liye) maine arz kya ke aey ameerul-momineen! mausame-Haj mein maamooli soojh-bojh rakhney waley sab tarah ke log jama hotey hain aur shor-ghul bahut hota hai. is liye mera khayal hai ke aap apna irada rok dein aur Madina pahunch kar (khitaab farmaaein) kyonke wo hijrat aur sunnat ka ghar hai aur wahan samajhdaar muazzaz aur saahibe-aql log rahtey hain.'' is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum theek kehtey ho, Madina pahunchtey hi sabse pehli fursat mein logon ko khitab karne ke liye zaroor khada hoonga."
3929,"jab Ansar ne muhajireen ki mezbaanii ke liye Qura daala to Usman bin Mazoon unke gharaaney ke hissey mein aaey they. Umme- Alaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan bimar pad gaey. maine unki poori tarah teemaardaarii ki wo na bach sakey. ham ne unhein unke kapdon mein lapet diya tha. itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif laey to maine kaha : abu-Saaib ! (Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat ( tum par Allah ki rahmatein hon, meri tumharey mutaalliq gawahi hai ke Allah Taala ne tumhen apne ikraam se nawaza hai. ye sun kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumhen ye kaisey malum hua ke Allah Taala ne unhein apne ikraam se nawaza hai? maine arz kya mujhey to is silsiley mein kuchh khabar nahi hai. mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon ya Rasulullah ! lekin aur kisey nawaazega? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usmein to waqei koi shak w shuba nahi ke aik yaqeeni Amr ( maut ( unko aa chuka hai. Allah ki qasm ke main bhi unke liye Allah Taala se khair-khahi ki ummeed rakhta hun lekin main halanke Allah ka rasool hun khud apne mutaalliq nahi jaan sakta ke mere sath kya mamla hoga. Umme- Alaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya phir Allah ki qasm ke iske baad main ab kisi ke barey mein uski paakii nahi karoongii. unhon-ne bayan kya ke is waaqie par mujhey bada ranj hua. phir main so gaee to maine khuwab mein dekha ke Usman bin Mazoon ke liye aik bahtaa hua chashma hai. main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aap se apna khuwab bayan kya to aap ne farmaya ke ye unka amal tha."
3930,Buaas ki ladai ko) Ansar ke qabaayel Aus w khazraj ke darmyan ( Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Madina mein aaney se pahley hi barpa kara diya tha chunanche jab aap Madina tashrif laey to Ansar mein phoot padi hui thi aur unke sardaar qatl ho chukey they. usmein Allah ki ye hikmat malum hoti hai ke Ansar Islam qabool kar lein.
3931,"Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi wahin tashrif rakhtey they eidul-fitr ya eidul-Azha ka din tha, 2 ladkiyan yaum Buaas ke barey mein wo ashaar padh rahi thin jo Ansar ke Shoaraa ne apne fakhr mein kahey they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ye shaitaanii gaaney baajey ! (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein) 2 martaba unhon-ne ye jumla dohraya , lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Abu-Bakar ! unhein chhod do. har qaum ki eid hoti hai aur hamari eid aaj ka ye din hai.''"
3932,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Madina ke buland taraf Quba ke aik mahalla mein aap ne (sab se pahley) qiyam kya jisey bani Amr-bin-Auf ka mahalla kaha jata tha. rawi ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan chaudah raat qiyam kya phir aap ne qabila banii-Najjaar ke logon ko bula bhejaa. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Ansar banii-Najjaar aap ki khidmat mein talwaarein latkaey huey hazir huey. rawi ne bayan kya maano us waqt bhi wo manzar meri nazron ke samney hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par Sawar hain. Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) usi sawari par aap ke peechhey sawar hain aur banii-Najjaar ke Ansar aap ke charon taraf halqa banaey huey asliha lekar paidal chaley ja rahe hain. aakhir aap Abu-Ayub Ansari ke ghar ke qareeb utar gaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke abhi tak jahan bhi Namaz ka waqt ho jata wahin aap Namaz padh letey they. bakriyon ke rewad jahan raat ko baandhey jatey wahan bhi Namaz padh li jati thi. bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ki tameer ka hukm farmaya, aap ne uske liye qabila banii-Najjaar ke logon ko bula bhejaa. wo hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey banu-Najjaar ! apne us baagh ki qeemat tay kar lo. '' unhon-ne arz kya nahi Allah ki qism ham uski qeemat Allah ke siwa aur kisi se nahi ley saktey. rawi ne bayan kya ke us baagh mein wo cheezein thin jo main tum se bayan karunga. usmein mushrekeen ki qabrein thin, kuchh usmein khandar tha aur khajooron ke darakht bhi they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se mushrekeen ki qabrein ukhaad di gain, jahan khandar tha usey barabar kya gaya aur khajooron ke darakht kaat diye gaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke khajoor ke taney masjid ki taraf aik qataar mein bataur diwar rakh diye gaey aur darwaza main (chaukhat ki jagah) patthar rakh diye. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke sahaba jab patthar la rahe they, to sher padhtey jatey they Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unke sath khud patthar latey aur sher padhtey. sahaba ye sher padhtey ke aey Allaah! aakhirat hi ki khair, khair hai, to to Ansar aur muhajireen ki madad farmaa."
3933,tum ne Makka main (muhaajir ke) thaharney ke mas'ale mein kya suna hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Alaa-bin-hizramii (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''muhaajir ko (Haj mein) tawaaf wadaa' ke baad teen din thaharney ki ijazat hai.''
3934,taareekh ka shumaar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nabwooat ke saal se hua aur na aap ki wafat ke saal se balke iska shumaar Madina ki hijrat ke saal se hua.
3935,(pahley ( Namaz sirf 2 rakaat farz hui thi phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hijrat ki to wo farz rakaat char rakaat ho gaiin. albatta safar ki haalat mein Namaz apni haalat mein baqi rakhi gaee. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Abdur-Razzaq ne Mamar se ki hai.
3936,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hijjatul-wada 10 hijri ke mauqe par meri mizaaj pursi ke liye tashrif laey. us marz mein mere bchney ki koi ummeed nahi rahi thi. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! marz ki shiddat aap khud dekh rahey hain, mere paas maal bahut hai aur sirf meri aik ladki waaris hai to kya main apne 2 tehai maal ka sadqa kar dun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. maine arz kya phir aadhey ka kar dun? farmaya ke Sad ! bas aik tehai ka kar do, ye bhi bahut hai. to agar apni aulad ko maaldaar chhod kar jaey to ye us se behtar hai ke unhein mohtaaj chhodey aur wo logon ke samney hath phailaatey phirein. Ahmed bin Yunus ne bayan kya, unse Ibrahim bin Sad ne ke tum apni aulad ko chhod kar jo kuchh bhi kharch karogey aur us se Allah Taala ki raza mandi maqsud hogi to Allah Taala tumhen iska sawab dega, Allah tumhen us luqme par bhi sawab dega jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein daalogey. maine puchha : ya Rasulullah! kya main apne sathiyon se peechhey Makka mein reh jaaunga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum peechhey nahi rahogey aur tum jo bhi amal karogey aur us se maqsud Allah Taala ki razaamandii hogi to tumhara martaba uski wjah se buland hota rahega aur shayad tum abhi bahut dinon tak zinda rahogey tum se bahut se logon ( musalmanon ( ko nafa pahunchega aur bahuton ko) ghair-muslimon ( nuqsan hoga. aey Allah ! mere sahaba ki hijrat poori kar de aur unhein ultey paon wapas na kar (ke wo hijrat ko chhod kar apne gharon ko wapas aa jayen ( albatta Sad bin Khaula nuqsan mein pad gaey aur Ahmed bin Yunus aur Musa bin Ismail ne us hadis ko Ibrahim bin Sad se riwayat kya usmein (apni aulad ko chhodo, ke bajaey) tum apne waarison ko chhodo ye alfaz marwi (bayan) hain."
3937,jab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) hijrat karke aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unka bhai-chara Sad-bin-Rabee Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath karaya tha. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke unke ahal w maal mein se aadha wo qabool kar lein lekin Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah Taala aap ke ahal w maal mein barkat de. aap to mujhey bazar ka rasta bata dein. chunanche unhon-ne tijarat shuru kar di aur pahley din unhein kuchh paneer aur ghi mein nafa mila. chand dinon ke baad unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke unke kapdon par) khushbu ki) zardi ka nishan hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Abdur-Rehman ye kya hai? unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine aik Ansari aurat se shadi kar li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein mehar main tum ne kya diya ? unhon-ne bataya ke aik guthli barabar sona . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab walima karo chahe aik hi bakri ka ho.
3938,"jab Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Madina aaney ki khabar hui to wo aap se chand sawal karne ke liye aaey. unhon-ne kaha ke main aap se teen chizon ke mutaalliq poochhunga jinhein Nabi ke siwa aur koi nahi janta. qiyamat ki sabse pehli nishani kya hogii? ahle-jannat ki ziyaafat sabse pahley kis khaney se ki jaeygi? aur kya baat hai ke bachcha kabhi bap par jata hai aur kabhi maan par? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jawab abhi mujhey Jibraeel ne aa kar bataya hai. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam ne kaha ke ye malaaika mein yahudiyon ke dushman hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ki pehli nishani aik aag hai jo insanon ko mashriq se maghrib ki taraf ley jaeygi. jis khaney se sabse pahley ahle-jannat ki ziyaafat hogi wo machhli ki kalejii ka badha hua tukda hoga (jo bahut hi lazeez aur jald Hazam honey wala hota hai) aur bachcha bap ki sura par us waqt jata hai jab aurat ke pani par mard ka pani ghalib aa jaey aur jab mard ke pani par aurat ka pani ghalib aa jaey to bachcha maan par jata hai. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain. phir unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Yahudi badey bohtan lagaaney waley log hain. isliye aap us se pahley ke mere Islam ke barey mein unhein kuchh malum ho, unse mere mutaalliq malum farmaaein. chunanche chand Yahudi aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tumhari qaum mein Abdullaah-bin-Salaam kon hain? wo kehney lagey ke ham mein sabse behtar aur sabse behtar ke betey hain, ham mein sabse afzal aur sabse afzal ke betey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumhara kya khayal hai agar wo Islam laaein ? wo kehney lagey us se Allah Taala unhein apni panah mein rakhey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara unse yahi sawal kya aur unhon-ne yahi jawab diya. iske baad Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) bahar aaey aur kaha, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain. ab wo kehney lagey ye to ham mein sabse badtar aadmi hain aur sabse badtar bap ke betey hain. fauran hi burai shuru kar di, Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! isi ka mujhey dar tha."
3939,"mere aik saajhii ne bazar mein chand dirham udhaar farokht kiye, maine us se kaha : sub'haan-Allaah! kya ye jaaiz hai? unhon-ne kaha : Subhan-Allah , Allah ki qism ! maine bazar mein usey bechaa to kisi ne bhi qaabile-aitiraaz nahi samjhaa. maine Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ( hijrat karke ( tashrif laey to is tarah khareed w farokht kya kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khareed w farokht ki is sura mein agar mamla dast-badast ( naqd (ho to koi muzaayqa nahi lekin agar udhaar par mamla kya to phir ye sura jaaiz nahi aur Zaid-bin-Arqam se bhi mil kar iske mutaalliq poochh lo kyonke wo ham mein badey sodagar they. maine Zaid-bin-Arqam se puchha to unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke Sufiyan ne aik martaba yun bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab hamarey yahan Madina tashrif laey to ham (is tarah ki) khareed w farokht kya kartey they aur bayan kya ke udhaar mausam tak ke liye ya ( yun bayan kya ke) Haj tak ke liye."
3940,"mere aik saajhii ne bazar mein chand dirham udhaar farokht kiye, maine us se kaha : sub'haan-Allaah! kya ye jaaiz hai? unhon-ne kaha : Subhan-Allah , Allah ki qism ! maine bazar mein usey bechaa to kisi ne bhi qaabile-aitiraaz nahi samjhaa. maine Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ( hijrat karke ( tashrif laey to is tarah khareed w farokht kya kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khareed w farokht ki is sura mein agar mamla dast-badast ( naqd (ho to koi muzaayqa nahi lekin agar udhaar par mamla kya to phir ye sura jaaiz nahi aur Zaid-bin-Arqam se bhi mil kar iske mutaalliq poochh lo kyonke wo ham mein badey sodagar they. maine Zaid-bin-Arqam se puchha to unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke Sufiyan ne aik martaba yun bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab hamarey yahan Madina tashrif laey to ham (is tarah ki) khareed w farokht kya kartey they aur bayan kya ke udhaar mausam tak ke liye ya ( yun bayan kya ke) Haj tak ke liye."
3941,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar das Yahudi (ahbaar w ulamaa) mujh par eman ley aatey to tamam yahood musalman ho jatey. ''
3942,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke Yahudi Aashooraa ke din ki ta'zeem kartey hain aur us din roza rakhtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham us din roza rakhney ke zyada haqdaar hain. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din ke rozey ka hukm diya.
3943,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke Yahudi Aashooraa ke din roza rakhtey hain. iske mutaalliq unse puchha gaya to unhon-ne bataya ke ye wo din hai jis mein Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) aur Bani-Israeel ko firaun par fateh inayat farmai thi chunanche ham us din ki ta'zeem mein roza rakhtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham Musa (Alaihissalam) se tumhaare muqable zyada qareeb hain aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din roza rakhney ka hukm diya.
3944,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar ke baal ko peshani par latkaa detey they aur mushrekeen maang nikaaltey they aur ahle-kitab bhi apne saron ke baal peshani par latkaey rehney detey they. jin maamlon main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) wahi ke zariie') koi hukm nahi hota tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unmein ahle-kitab ki muwafiqat pasand kartey they. phir baad main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi maang nikalney lagey they.
3945,"wo ahle-kitab hi to hain jinhoney aasmani kitab ko tukdey tukdey kar daalaa, kuchh baton par eman laey aur kuchh baton ka inkar kya."
3946,"unko kuchh uper das aadmiyon ne aik Malik se unko das se zayed aadmiyon ne liya, aik Malik ne doosrey Malik se khareedaa ."
3947,main raam Hurmuz (Faaras mein aik maqam hai) ka rehney wala hun.
3948,Esa (Alaihissalam) aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan mein) فترة (ka zamana (yani jis mein koi paighambar nahi aayaa) 600 baras ka waqfa guzra hai.
